20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kishan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107047-ishan-kishan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Till%20very%20recently%2C%20the%20star%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20duo%20was%20part%20of%20the%20side.%20While%20Ishan%20Kishan%20was%20last%20part%20of%20the%20Test%20squad%20during%20India's%20Tour%20of%20South%20Africa%20in%20December%2C%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20played%20the%20first%20two%20Tests%20of%20the%20ongoing%20series%20against%20England.%20Yet%2C%20the%20BCCI%20removed%20the%20two%20senior%20player%20from%20the%20contracts%20list.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20BCCI%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20single%20out%20the%20duo's%20absence%20with%20the%20following%20line%20in%20the%20list%3A%20%26quot%3BPlease%20note%20that%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20and%20Ishan%20Kishan%20were%20not%20considered%20for%20the%20annual%20contracts%20in%20this%20round%20of%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20were%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20dropped%20from%20BCCI's%20Annual%20Player%20Contracts%20for%20Team%20India%20(Senior%20Men)%20for%20the%202023-24%20season%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIshan%20Kishan's%20case%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20was%20no%20official%20reason%20given%20on%20why%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20were%20dropped%2C%20one%20line%20in%20BCCI's%20release%20gives%20a%20strong%20hint.%20%26quot%3BThe%20BCCI%20has%20recommended%20that%20all%20athletes%20give%20precedence%20to%20participating%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20during%20periods%20when%20they%20are%20not%20representing%20the%20national%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BCCI%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ishan%20Kishan%20had%20left%20India's%20Tour%20of%20South%20Africa%2C%20the%20BCCI%20had%20said%20on%20December%2017%3A%20%26quot%3BMr%20Ishan%20Kishan%20has%20requested%20the%20BCCI%20to%20be%20released%20from%20the%20upcoming%20Test%20series%20against%20South%20Africa%20citing%20personal%20reasons.%20The%20wicket-keeper%20has%20subsequently%20been%20withdrawn%20from%20the%20Test%20squad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20was%20expected%20that%20Ishan%20Kishan%20would%20play%20domestic%20cricket%20from%20his%20time%20away%20from%20the%20national%20team%2C%20the%20wicketkeeper-batter%20chose%20to%20remain%20absent%20from%20his%20state%20team%20Jharkhand's%20Ranji%20Trophy%20matches.%20Despite%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20clearly%20mentioning%20that%20he%20need%20to%20play%20some%20form%20of%20cricket%20to%20regain%20his%20place%20in%C2%A0%20the%20Indian%20squad%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan%20ignored%20the%20instruction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20he%20only%20made%20a%20return%20to%20competitive%20cricket%20on%20Tuesday%20at%20the%20DY%20Patil%20T20%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBCCI%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20had%20also%20mentioned%20that%20it%20is%20mandatory%20for%20centrally%20contracted%20players%2C%20who%20are%20not%20in%20the%20national%20team%2C%20to%20play%20red-ball%20cricket.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShreyas%20Iyer's%20case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20middle%20order%20batter%20has%20been%20battling%20poor%20form%20in%20Test%20cricket.%20He%20was%20dropped%20from%20the%20last%20three%20Tests%20against%20England%20after%20failing%20to%20leave%20a%20mark%20in%20the%20first%20two%20games.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIf%20Shreyas%20was%20to%20be%20rested%20because%20of%20injury%2C%20the%20BCCI%20medical%20bulletin%20would%20have%20had%20an%20update.%20Since%20there%20are%20no%20updates%2C%20it%20can%20be%20concluded%20that%20he%20has%20got%20the%20axe%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20had%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20then.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20Iyer%20made%20himself%20unavailable%20for%20Mumbai's%20Ranji%20Trophy%20quarterfinals%20citing%20injury%20concerns%20but%20the%20National%20Cricket%20Academy%20(NCA)%20has%20said%20that%20he%20has%20no%20'fresh%20injuries'%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Indian%20Express.%20The%20report%20cited%20an%20email%20from%20Nitin%20Patel%2C%20the%20head%20of%20sports%20science%20and%20medicine%20at%20the%20NCA%2C%20who%20told%20selectors%20that%20Iyer%20was%20'fit'.%20It%20also%20quoted%20Mumbai%20Cricket%20Association%20sources%20saying%20that%20Iyer%20had%20cited%20back%20pain%20as%20the%20reason%20behind%20missing%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20quarterfinal%20match%20against%20Baroda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShreyas%20Iyer%20was%20fit%20and%20available%20for%20selection%20as%20per%20the%20handover%20report%20of%20the%20Indian%20team%20after%20the%202nd%20Test%20match%20against%20England.%20There%20are%20currently%20no%20fresh%20injuries%20reported%20as%20well%20after%20his%20departure%20from%20Team%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Patel%20wrote%20in%20his%20email%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20BCCI%20omitting%20both%20from%20its%20contract%20list%2C%20the%20national%20body%20might%20be%20acting%20tough%20to%20a%20send%20a%20stern%20message%20to%20all%20players%20who%20has%20national%20team%20aspiration%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709127120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fsm30qqc8_ishan-kishan-shreyas-iyer_625x300_28_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwhy-ishan-kishan-and-shreyas-iyer-were-axed-from-bcci-contract-list-a-case-of-bcci-acting-tough-explained-5144453%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20prominent%20players%20-%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20-%20have%20not%20been%20included%20by%20BCCI%20in%20its%20Annual%20Player%20Contracts%20for%20Team%20India%20(Senior%20Men)%20for%20the%202023-24%20season%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Several%20killed%20in%20attack%20on%20security%20HQ%20in%20Chad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709127087000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F9156%2Fproduction%2F_132760273_gettyimages-1241079378.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68424115%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20assault%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20Chad%20announced%20a%20date%20for%20presidential%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68424115%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68424115.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68424115.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmer%20Stopped%20At%20Bengaluru%20Metro%20For%20%26quot%3BUntidy%26quot%3B%20Clothes%2C%20Rights%20Body%20Says...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20after%20a%20farmer%20was%20stopped%20from%20boarding%20a%20metro%20train%20by%20an%20official%20at%20Bengaluru's%20Rajajinagar%20station%20because%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Buntidy%26quot%3B%20clothes%2C%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20has%20taken%20suo%20motu%20cognizance%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NHRC%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20said%20it%20has%20observed%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20contents%20of%20the%20media%20report%2C%20if%20true%2C%20amount%20to%20a%20violation%20of%20human%20rights%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BNo%20person%20can%20be%20denied%20access%20to%20public%20transport%20based%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20clothes%20he%20or%20she%20is%20wearing.%20If%20someone%20possesses%20any%20objectionable%20material%2C%20he%20could%20be%20stopped%20only%20as%20per%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%20has%20issued%20notices%20to%20the%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Secretary%20and%20the%20Managing%20Director%20of%20Bengaluru%20Metro%20Rail%20Corporation%20Limited%20(BMRCL)%20and%20asked%20for%20a%20detailed%20report%20within%20four%20weeks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20should%20include%20steps%20taken%20or%20proposed%20to%20ensure%20such%20incidents%20do%20not%20recur%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rights%20body%20also%20posted%20about%20the%20incident%20on%20X%20and%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BNHRC%20takes%20suo%20motu%20cognizance%20of%20the%20reported%20stopping%20of%20a%20farmer%20from%20boarding%20the%20metro%20train%20by%20an%20official%20due%20to%20his%20untidy%20attire.%20The%20Commission%20observes%20no%20one%20can%20be%20denied%20access%20to%20public%20transport%20based%20on%20his%20attire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENHRC%20takes%20suo%20motu%20cognizance%20of%20the%20reported%20stopping%20of%20a%20farmer%20from%20boarding%20the%20metro%20train%20by%20an%20official%20due%20to%20his%20untidy%20attire.%20The%20Commission%20observes%20no%20one%20can%20be%20denied%20access%20to%20public%20transport%20based%20on%20his%20attire.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FHefTV3nPy5%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FHefTV3nPy5%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20NHRC%20India%20(%40India_NHRC)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndia_NHRC%2Fstatus%2F1762813127626805676%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2028%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2026%2C%20a%20farmer%20with%20a%20large%20sack%20on%20his%20head%20was%20stopped%20by%20an%20official%20at%20the%20baggage%20checkpoint%20inside%20the%20Rajajinagar%20metro%20station%20and%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20platform%20even%20though%20he%20had%20a%20ticket.%20The%20video%20of%20the%20incident%20is%20now%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20commuters%20were%20heard%20in%20the%20video%20protesting%20the%20official's%20decision.%20They%20asked%20the%20official%20if%20the%20metro%20rail%20has%20a%20dress%20code%20for%20passengers%20and%20whether%20the%20rail%20service%20is%20only%20meant%20for%20VIPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmer%20was%20later%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20platform%20and%20authorities%20expressed%20regret%20over%20the%20incident.%C2%A0Bengaluru's%20Namma%20Metro%20dismissed%20the%20official%20after%20the%20video%20sparked%20massive%20outrage%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709127060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fn7fu6krg_farmer-stopped-at-bengaluru-metro_625x300_28_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmer-stopped-at-bengaluru-metro-for-untidy-clothes-rights-body-nhrc-says-5144452%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20after%20a%20farmer%20was%20stopped%20from%20boarding%20a%20metro%20train%20by%20an%20official%20at%20Bengaluru's%20Rajajinagar%20station%20because%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Buntidy%26quot%3B%20clothes%2C%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20has%20taken%20suo%20motu%20cognizance%20of%20the%20incident.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmer-stopped-at-bengaluru-metro-for-untidy-clothes-rights-body-nhrc-says-5144452%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmer-stopped-at-bengaluru-metro-for-untidy-clothes-rights-body-nhrc-says-5144452%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmer-stopped-at-bengaluru-metro-for-untidy-clothes-rights-body-nhrc-says-5144452%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shreyas%20Iyer%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan%20Dropped%20From%20BCCI%20Annual%20Contract%20List%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20on%20Wednesday%20announced%20the%20Annual%20Player%20Contracts%20for%20Team%20India%20(Senior%20Men)%20for%20the%202023-24%20season%20(October%201st%2C%202023%20to%20September%2030th%2C%202024).%20The%20major%20omissions%20from%20the%20list%20were%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20star%20duo%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20and%20Ishan%20Kishan.%20%26quot%3BPlease%20note%20that%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20and%20Ishan%20Kishan%20were%20not%20considered%20for%20the%20annual%20contracts%20in%20this%20round%20of%20recommendations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BCCI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20enough%20speculations%20about%20the%20duo%20being%20dropped%20from%20the%20BCCI%20contract%20list.%20Ishan%20Kishan%20took%20a%20break%20midway%20into%20India's%20Tour%20of%20South%20Africa.%20After%20that%20Ishan%20Kishan%20was%20not%20picked%20for%20the%20T20I%20series%20at%20home%20against%20Afghanistan%20and%20the%20Test%20series%20against%20England.%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20head%20coach%20Rahul%20Dravid%20made%20it%20absolutely%20clear%20that%20Ishan%20Kishan%20had%20to%20play%20some%20form%20of%20the%20game%20to%20make%20a%20return%20to%20the%20national%20team.%20However%2C%20he%20kept%20on%20missing%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20matches%20for%20his%20state%20team%20Jharkhand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShreyas%20Iyer%20recently%20excused%20himself%20from%20a%20Ranji%20Trophy%20game%20of%20Mumbai%20due%20to%20a%20back%20issue.%20A%20report%20in%20the%20Times%20of%20India%20had%20predicted%20that%20the%20duo%20will%20be%20dropped%20from%20the%20BCCI%20contracts%20list.%20%26quot%3BKishan%20and%20Iyer%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20excluded%20from%20that%20list%2C%20as%20both%20haven't%20been%20playing%20domestic%20cricket%20despite%20the%20BCCI's%20diktat%20to%20do%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20told%20the%20paper.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20among%20the%20other%20players%20-%C2%A0Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20were%20placed%20in%C2%A0%20the%20highest%20-%20A%2B%20-%20category.%20Six%20players%20-%20R%20Ashwin%2C%20Mohd.%20Shami%2C%20Mohd.%20Siraj%2C%20KL%20Rahul%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%20-%20are%20in%20the%20A%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20athletes%20who%20meet%20the%20criteria%20of%20playing%20a%20minimum%20of%203%20Tests%20or%208%20ODIs%20or%2010%20T20Is%20within%20the%20specified%20period%20will%20automatically%20be%20included%20in%20Grade%20C%20on%20a%20pro-rata%20basis.%20For%20instance%2C%20Dhruv%20Jurel%20and%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%2C%20having%20played%202%20Test%20matches%20so%20far%2C%20will%20be%20inducted%20into%20Grade%20C%20if%20they%20participate%20in%20the%20Dharamsala%20Test%20Match%2C%20i.e.%2C%20the%205th%20Test%20of%20the%20ongoing%20series%20against%20England%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BCCI%20released%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Selection%20Committee%20has%20also%20recommended%20Fast%20Bowling%20contracts%20for%20the%20following%20athletes%20%E2%80%93%20Akash%20Deep%2C%20Vijaykumar%20Vyshak%2C%20Umran%20Malik%2C%20Yash%20Dayal%20and%20Vidwath%20Kaverappa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BCCI%20has%20recommended%20that%20all%20athletes%20give%20precedence%20to%20participating%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20during%20periods%20when%20they%20are%20not%20representing%20the%20national%20team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFull%20list%20of%20BCCI%20contractes%20players%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrade%20A%2B%20(4%20Athletes)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrade%20A%20(6%20Athletes)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ER%20Ashwin%2C%20Mohd.%20Shami%2C%20Mohd.%20Siraj%2C%20KL%20Rahul%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3