n%20a%20fire%20hose%20of%20secondhand%20trauma%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20look%20away.%20Meanwhile%2C%20this%20deeply%20disturbing%20content%20would%20come%20alongside%20cheerful%20recipe%20ideas%2C%20clothing%20ads%2C%20and%20memes%20about%20husbands%20spending%20too%20much%20time%20in%20the%20bathroom%20(%23relatable).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20felt%20like%20an%20insane%2C%20frenetic%20way%20to%20consume%20information%2C%20and%20it%20was%20seriously%20impacting%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-productivity-tip-helped-me-focus-careers-strategy-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20focus%20at%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20my%20ability%20to%20be%20present%20for%20my%20child.%20Still%2C%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20stop%20using%20the%20app%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEventually%2C%20I%20came%20to%20a%20compromise%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20now%20delete%20Instagram%20every%20morning%20and%20then%20reinstall%20it%20at%20night.%20In%20the%20best%20case%2C%20I%20hold%20out%20until%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-toddler-sometimes-goes-to-bed-at-10-pm-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etoddler%20has%20gone%20to%20bed%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20way%2C%20I%20can%20quickly%20catch%20up%20on%20the%20few%20posts%20my%20actual%20friends%20have%20shared%20and%20feel%20somewhat%20in%20the%20loop%20with%20what's%20trending%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20I'd%20tried%20limiting%20my%20app%20use%20by%20setting%20time%20limits.%20On%20iPhones%2C%20a%20section%20within%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-limit-screen-time-on-iphone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESettings%26quot%3B%20called%20%26quot%3BScreen%20Time%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20allows%20you%20to%20set%20time%20limits%20for%20any%20app.%20The%20problem%3A%20It%20was%20way%20too%20easy%20for%20me%20to%20get%20past%20the%20setting%20%E2%80%94%20you%20simply%20need%20to%20enter%20y