%2C%22author%22%3A%22bnolan%40insider.com%20(Beatrice%20Nolan%2CHugh%20Langley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-bias-sundar-pichai-memo-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20FTC%20is%20going%20to%20war%20with%20tax%20services%20that%20bill%20themselves%20as%20free%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225632%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22protestors%20holding%20up%20signs%20against%20H%26amp%3BR%20Block%20and%20TurboTax%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65de575590413ab8e1d74499%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223808%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EProtestors%20gather%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%20in%202023%20to%20advocate%20for%20simpler%20tax%20services.%3Cp%3ETasos%20Katopodis%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20FTC%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20H%26amp%3BR%20Block%20over%20what%20the%20commission%20called%20deceptive%20advertising.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20alleges%20that%20H%26amp%3BR%20Block%20tricks%20users%20into%20starting%20with%20a%20higher-cost%20service%2C%20making%20downgrading%20difficult.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20follows%20a%20similar%20FTC%20action%20against%20Intuit%20for%20misleading%20practices%20with%20its%20TurboTax%20service.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESo-called%20%26quot%3Bfree%26quot%3B%20online%20tax%20filing%20services%20like%20Intuit's%20TurboTax%20and%20H%26amp%3BR%20Block's%20Online%20Filing%20option%20have%2C%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20not%20actually%20been%20free%20for%20many%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20FTC%20has%20now%20committed%20to%20taking%20them%20on%20one%20by%20one%20%E2%80%94%20most%20recently%20with%20a%20new%20lawsuit%20against%20H%26amp%3BR%20Block.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consumer%20protection%20agency%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftc.gov%2Fsystem%2Ffiles%2Fftc_gov%2Fpdf%2Fd09427hrblockadmincomplaintpublic.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiled%20a%20complaint%20against%20H%26amp%3BR%20Block%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%2C%20accusing%20the%20company%20of%20deceptive%20advertising%20and%20unfairly%20deleting%20users'%20tax%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BH%26amp%3BR%20Block%20designed%20its%20online%20products%20to%20present%20an%20obstacle%20course%20of%20tedious%20challenges%20to%20consumers%2C%20pressuring%20them%20into%20overpaying%20for%20its%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20Samuel%20Levine%2C%20the%20Director%20of%20the%20FTC's%20Bureau%20of%20Consumer%20Protection%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftc.gov%2Fnews-events%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2F2024%2F02%2Fftc-takes-action-against-tax-prep-company-hr-block-wiping-consumers-data-deceptively-marketing-free%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday's%20action%20demonstrates%20that%20companies%20using%20coercive%20techniques%20that%20harm%20consumers%20can%20expect%20to%20hear%20from%20the%20FTC%2C%26quot%3B%20Levine%20continued.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20complaint%2C%20the%20FTC%20alleges%20that%20H%26amp%3BR%20Block's%20online%20filing%20system%20leads%20users%20to%20start%20off%20with%20a%20higher-cost%20service%2C%20having%20them%20spend%20time%20entering%20all%20their%20tax%20information%20before%20they%20realize%20later%20on%20in%20the%20process%20that%20they%20can%20actually%20downgrade%20to%20a%20free%20or%20lower-cost%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20when%20they%20try%20to%20downgrade%2C%20they%20are%20met%20with%20a%20series%20of%20time-consuming%20challenges%2C%20according%20to%20the%20FTC's%20statement.%20The%20system%20deletes%20all%20the%20data%20the%20user%20had%20just%20painstakingly%20entered%2C%20telling%20them%20to%20instead%20contact%20a%20customer%20service%20agent%20to%20access%20the%20downgraded%20option%2C%20which%20makes%20them%20start%20all%20over%20again.%20In%20contrast%2C%20when%20a%20user%20wants%20to%20upgrade%20their%20service%2C%20the%20process%20is%20instant%20and%20seamless%2C%20the%20FTC%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FTC's%20complaint%20also%20accused%20H%26amp%3BR%20Block%20of%20deceptively%20advertising%20a%20%26quot%3Bfree%26quot%3B%20service%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20many%20users%20do%20not%20even%20qualify%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20allegations%2C%20H%26amp%3BR%20Block's%20chief%20legal%20officer%20Dara%20Redler%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20company%20provides%20%26quot%3Ba%20great%20deal%20of%20value%2C%20unmatched%20tax%20expertise%2C%20and%20fair%20and%20transparent%20pricing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20H%26amp%3BR%20Block%20allows%20consumers%20to%20downgrade%20to%20a%20less-expensive%20DIY%20Product%20via%20multiple%20mechanisms%20while%20ensuring%20the%20preparation%20of%20accurate%20tax%20returns%2C%26quot%3B%20Redler's%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20all%20this%20sounds%20familiar%2C%20that's%20because%20it%20is.%20The%20FTC%20has%20also%20taken%20on%20Intuit%2C%20the%20maker%20of%20TurboTax%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20misleading%20practices.%20The%20consumer%20agency%20first%20sued%20Intuit%20in%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturbotax-cant-advertise-as-free-when-many-pay-ftc-ruling-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinally%20ruling%20in%20January%20of%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20company%20cannot%20advertise%20its%20services%20as%20%26quot%3Bfree%26quot%3B%20unless%20all%20consumers%20qualify%2C%20or%20the%20ads%20clearly%20say%20who%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntuit%20is%20appealing%20the%20FTC's%20ruling%2C%20and%20company%20spokesperson%20Derrick%20L.%20Plummer%20said%20in%20a%20statement%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2024%2F01%2F23%2F1226291903%2Fturbotax-intuit-ftc-free-services%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20to%20NPR%