r%20Himachal%2C%20Assam%20Jolt%20For%20Congress%20As%20Working%20Chief%20Quits%2C%20Eyes%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelivering%20another%20jolt%20to%20the%20Congress%20after%20the%20exit%20of%20leaders%20like%20former%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Chavan%20and%20former%20MP%20Milind%20Deora%2C%20the%20party's%20Assam%20working%20president%20has%20quit%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20join%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%20Goswami%2C%20a%20former%20MLA%20from%20Jorhat%2C%20announced%20his%20resignation%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20Congress%20General%20Secretary%20(Organisation)%20KC%20Venugopal%20on%20Wednesday.%20He%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20beg%20to%20state%20that%20I%20am%20tendering%20my%20resignation%20as%20the%20working%20President%20of%20Assam%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20and%20as%20an%20active%20member%20of%20Indian%20National%20Congress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20Mr%20Goswami%20is%20now%20in%20New%20Delhi%20where%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20meet%20BJP%20President%20JP%20Nadda%20and%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma.%20The%20party's%20core%20group%20from%20Assam%20and%20the%20national%20leadership%20are%20meeting%20in%20the%20capital%20to%20decide%20on%20candidates%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20the%20state%20and%20to%20take%20a%20call%20on%20how%20many%20seats%20should%20be%20left%20for%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goswami%20was%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20making%20preparations%20for%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20in%20Assam%20and%20had%20been%20questioned%20by%20the%20police%20a%20few%20days%20ago%20after%20a%20case%20was%20filed%20over%20deviating%20from%20the%20route%20for%20the%20march.%20On%20Sunday%2C%20however%2C%20the%20former%20MLA%20had%20quit%20as%20the%20organisational%20in-charge%20in%20Upper%20Assam%20citing%20%26quot%3Bvarious%20political%20reasons%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20another%20Congress%20working%20president%2C%20Kamalakhya%20Dey%20Purkayastha%2C%20had%20resigned%20and%20extended%20his%20support%20to%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20state.%20He%20was%20joined%20by%20fellow%20Congress%20MLA%20Basanta%20Das.%20Excluding%20them%2C%20the%20Congress%20now%20has%20only%2023%20MLAs%20in%20the%20126-member%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goswami's%20exit%20will%20add%20to%20the%20Congress's%20troubles%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0The%20party%20faced%20a%20shock%20defeat%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20poll%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20is%20now%20grappling%20with%20the%20possibility%20of%20its%20government%20being%20toppled%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20only%20state%20in%20north%20India%20where%20it%20is%20in%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssam%20sends%2014%20MPs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%20nine%20seats%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'State%20Reasons'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20Mr%20Goswami's%20resignation%2C%20Congress%20MLA%20and%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Assam%2C%20Debabrata%20Saikia%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRana%20Goswami%20was%20a%20very%20senior%20leader.%20He%20rose%20in%20the%20party%20from%20the%20grassroots.%20He%20was%20a%20two-time%20MLA%20and%20also%20worked%20at%20the%20national%20level.%20I%20think%20the%20Congress%20has%20given%20him%20whatever%20it%20could%20as%20a%20dedicated%20party%20worker.%20He%20must%20have%20been%20dissatisfied%20or%20there%20may%20be%20some%20other%20things%2C%20which%20we%20don't%20know%2C%20that%20compelled%20him%20to%20leave%20a%20party%20he%20has%20served%20for%20so%20long.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20appeal%20to%20him%20is%20to%20state%20the%20reasons%20for%20leaving%20the%20party.%20If%20he%20tells%20us%2C%20we%20can%20act%20on%20his%20grievances%20and%20the%20party%20can%20grow.%20Opposition%20is%20a%20must%20in%20Indian%20democracy%20and%20we%20cannot%20allow%20an%20opposition-free%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Saikia%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Mr%20Purkayastha's%20support%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20Mr%20Saikia%20claimed%20he%20was%20harassed%20by%20the%20vigilance%20department%20during%20the%20Durga%20Puja%20festival%20last%20year.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20under%20severe%20pressure%20and%20was%20compelled%20to%20go%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Kamalakhya%20resigned%20as%20he%20could%20not%20withstand%20the%20assault%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20other%20agencies%20in%20bogus%20cases.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Will%20Welcome%20Him'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Sarma%20was%20asked%20on%20Tuesday%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20Mr%20Goswami%20joining%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20had%20denied%20having%20any%20such%20information%2C%20but%20said%2C%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BHe%20is%20a%20powerful%20leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20if%20he%20joins%20the%20BJP%2C%20I%20will%20welcome%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHinting%20that%20several%20other%20Congress%20MLAs%20could%20join%20his%20party%2C%20Mr%20Sarma%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20only%20a%20few%20Muslim%20MLAs%20would%20remain%20in%20the%20Assam%20Congress%20by%20the%20time%20the%20next%20Assembly%20elections%20are%20held%20in%20the%20state%20in%202026.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709123520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F35066o4_rana-goswami-facebook_625x300_26_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frana-goswami-congress-crisis-after-himachal-congress-jolted-in-assam-as-working-president-quits-may-join-bjp-5144129%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delivering%20another%20jolt%20to%20the%20Congress%20after%20the%20exit%20of%20leaders%20like%20former%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Chavan%20and%20senior%20leader%20Milind%20Deora%2C%20the%20party's%20Assam%20working%20president%20has%20quit%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20join%20the%20BJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frana-goswami-congress-crisis-after-himachal-congress-jolted-in-assam-as-working-president-quits-may-join-bjp-5144129%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frana-goswami-congress-crisis-after-himachal-congress-jolted-in-assam-as-working-president-quits-may-join-bjp-5144129%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frana-goswami-congress-crisis-after-himachal-congress-jolted-in-assam-as-working-president-quits-may-join-bjp-5144129%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Disconcerting%20Trend%20Over%20the%20Undermining%20of%20Scientific%20Institutions%2C%20Threat%20to%20Scientific%20Temper'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28175801%2Fimage-1880.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20group%20of%20former%20scientists%20and%20academicians%20have%20raised%20concerns%20over%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdisconcerting%20trend%20of%20undermining%20scientific%20institutions%20and%20the%20constitutional%20idea%20of%20promoting%20scientific%20temper.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20abrupt%20closure%20of%20key%20institutions%20engaged%20in%20science%20communication%20to%20the%20promotion%20of%20pseudoscience%2C%20compounded%20by%20significant%20delays%20in%20the%20disbursement%20of%20funds%20and%20changes%20in%20school%20science%20syllabi%2C%20India%20is%20witnessing%20a%20systematic%20threat%20to%20its%20scientific%20foundation%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said%20in%20a%20panel%20discussion%20on%20February%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20discussion%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98Decoding%20Threat%20to%20Science%20and%20Scientific%20Temper%E2%80%99%2C%20was%20organised%20by%20%E2%80%98In%20Defence%20of%20Science%E2%80%99%20group%2C%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20raised%20concerns%20over%20key%20institutions%20like%20Vigyan%20Prasar%20and%20NISTADS%20being%20abruptly%20closed%20or%20merged%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20move%20diminished%20avenues%20for%20science%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20unique%20institutions%20in%20the%20developing%20world%20and%20had%20accumulated%20vast%20expertise%20in%20their%20respective%20areas%20of%20work.%20Another%20science%20outreach%20organisation%2C%20the%20Indian%20Science%20Congress%20Association%20(ISCA)%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20official%20apathy.%20The%20loss%20of%20these%20institutions%20will%20have%20far-reaching%20implications%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20scientific%20capabilities%20and%20global%20standing%20in%20the%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20speakers%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20pseudoscience%20endorsed%20by%20official%20agencies%20jeopardises%20public%20trust%20and%20undermines%20genuine%20scientific%20expertise%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEqually%20troubling%20is%20the%20promotion%20of%20pseudoscience%20over%20evidence-based%20research%20and%20established%20scientific%20principles.%20With%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20endorsement%20of%20unproven%20remedies%20and%20practices%20by%20official%20agencies%20and%20their%20funding%20by%20national%20research%20funding%20agencies%2C%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20of%20misleading%20the%20public%20and%20eroding%20trust%20in%20genuine%20scientific%20expertise.%20Such%20actions%20not%20only%20undermine%20public%20trust%20in%20science%2C%20and%20people%E2%80%99s%20health%20and%20safety%20but%20also%20jeopardize%20the%20credibility%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20scientific%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20said%20that%20bureaucratic%20delays%20in%20funding%20disbursement%20hamper%20research%20initiatives%2C%20while%20changes%20to%20school%20science%20syllabi%20prioritize%20ideological%20agendas%20over%20factual%20accuracy%2C%20hindering%20scientific%20literacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EReproduced%20below%20is%20the%20full%20statement.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStatement%20released%20by%20Scientists%20and%20Concerned%20Citizens%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%2C%20February%2026%2C%202024%3A%20Developments%20in%20recent%20years%20in%20India%20have%20caused%20concern%20within%20the%20scientific%20community%20and%20academic%20circles%2C%20pointing%20to%20a%20disconcerting%20trend%20of%20undermining%20scientific%20institutions%20and%20the%20constitutional%20idea%20of%20promoting%20scientific%20temper.%20From%20the%20abrupt%20closure%20of%20key%20institutions%20engaged%20in%20science%20communication%20to%20the%20promotion%20of%20pseudoscience%2C%20compounded%20by%20significant%20delays%20in%20the%20disbursement%20of%20funds%20and%20changes%20in%20school%20science%20syllabi%2C%20India%20is%20witnessing%20a%20systematic%20threat%20to%20its%20scientific%20foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20closure%20of%20Vigyan%20Prasar%20(VP)%2C%20which%20was%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20groundbreaking%20science%20communication%20and%20science%20popularisation%20efforts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20merger%20of%20the%20National%20Institute%20for%20Science%2C%20Technology%20and%20Development%20Studies%20(NISTADS)%20with%20a%20new%20entity%2C%20seem%20to%20be%20directed%20at%20ending%20the%20only%20avenues%20of%20connecting%20science%20with%20society%20through%20well-informed%20channels.%20They%20were%20unique%20institutions%20in%20the%20developing%20world%20and%20had%20accumulated%20vast%20expertise%20in%20their%20respective%20areas%20of%20work.%20Another%20science%20outreach%20organisation%2C%20the%20Indian%20Science%20Congress%20Association%20(ISCA)%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20official%20apathy.%20The%20loss%20of%20these%20institutions%20will%20have%20far-reaching%20implications%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20scientific%20capabilities%20and%20global%20standing%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEqually%20troubling%20is%20the%20promotion%20of%20pseudoscience%20over%20evidence-based%20research%20and%20established%20scientific%20principles.%20With%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20endorsement%20of%20unproven%20remedies%20and%20practices%20by%20official%20agencies%20and%20their%20funding%20by%20national%20research%20funding%20agencies%2C%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20of%20misleading%20the%20public%20and%20eroding%20trust%20in%20genuine%20scientific%20expertise.%20Such%20actions%20not%20only%20undermine%20public%20trust%20in%20science%2C%20and%20people%E2%80%99s%20health%20and%20safety%20but%20also%20jeopardize%20the%20credibility%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20scientific%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20bureaucratic%20delays%20in%20the%20disbursement%20of%20funds%20for%20scientific%20research%20projects%20and%20fellowships%20have%20left%20many%20young%20scientists%20and%20researchers%20in%20a%20precarious%20position.%20Without%20adequate%20funding%2C%20vital%20research%20initiatives%20are%20being%20hampered%2C%20leading%20to%20setbacks%20in%20critical%20areas.%20The%20decline%20in%20the%20budget%20allocated%20to%20science%20and%20higher%20education%20in%20general%2C%20and%20civilian%20R%26amp%3BD%20in%20particular%2C%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20does%20not%20augur%20well%20for%20Indian%20science%20as%20well%20as%20society.%20The%20continuous%20erosion%20of%20academic%20freedom%20is%20another%20matter%20of%20concern.%20All%20this%20could%20jeopardize%20India%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20address%20pressing%20societal%20challenges%20and%20capitalize%20on%20emerging%20opportunities%20using%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20these%20challenges%2C%20changes%20to%20school%20science%20syllabi%20have%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20quality%20and%20accuracy%20of%20science%20education%20in%20India.%20Alterations%20that%20prioritize%20ideological%20agendas%20over%20scientific%20facts%20risk%20hindering%20the%20development%20of%20a%20scientifically%20literate%20populace.%20This%20could%20have%20long-term%20implications%20for%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20foster%20a%20culture%20of%20innovation%20and%20critical%20thinking%20among%20its%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20advocates%20for%20evidence-based%20decision-making%20and%20scientific%20integrity%2C%20we%20feel%20that%20safeguarding%20scientific%20institutions%2C%20promoting%20rigorous%20research%20practices%2C%20ensuring%20timely%20funding%2C%20and%20upholding%20the%20integrity%20of%20science%20education%20are%20paramount%20to%20using%20science%20and%20technology%20for%20national%20development%2C%20and%20for%20the%20global%20competitiveness%20of%20Indian%20R%26amp%3BD.%20We%20urge%20the%20citizens%20to%20raise%20their%20voices%20against%20these%20disturbing%20trends.%20It%20is%20our%20constitutional%20duty%20to%20protect%20scientific%20institutions%20and%20promote%20scientific%20temper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EName%20Designation%20Affiliation%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEr.%20Anuj%20Sinha%20Former%20Scientist%20In-charge%20NCSTC%20(DST)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Director%20Vigyan%20Prasar%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Ashok%20Jain%20Former%20Director%20CSIR-NISTADS%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20D%20Raghunandan%2C%20Delhi%20Science%20Forum%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProf.%20Dinesh%20Abrol%20Former%20Chief%20Scientist%20CSIR-NISTADS%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Dinesh%20C%20Sharma%20Journalist%20%26amp%3B%20Author%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProf.%20Gauhar%20Raza%20Former%20Chief%20Scientist%20CSIR-NISCAIR%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Harshavardhana%20Hegde%20Orthopaedic%20Surgeon%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProf.%20Nandita%20Narain%20Former%20Head%20Mathematics%20Dept.%20Delhi%20University%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProf.%20N%20Raghuram%20GGSIU%2C%20Delhi%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERakesh%20Andania%2C%20Science%20Filmmaker%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Surjit%20Singh%2C%20Adjunct%20Prof.%20SIASTE%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ET%20V%20Venkateswaran%20Former%20Ac