0omelet%20packed%20with%20vegetables%2C%20herbs%2C%20and%20spices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20starts%20by%20air-frying%20some%20sweet%20potatoes%2C%20butternut%20squash%2C%20and%20zucchini%20and%20grabbing%20some%20frozen%20edamame%20beans%20out%20of%20the%20freezer.%20When%20frying%20the%20eggs%2C%20she%20adds%20the%20vegetables%20into%20the%20pan%20along%20with%20some%20butter%20beans%20for%20protein%20and%20fiber%2C%20smoked%20paprika%2C%20cumin%2C%20chipotle%2C%20chile%20flakes%2C%20and%20dried%20mixed%20herbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20side%2C%20she'll%20have%20some%20crispy%20kale.%20To%20make%20it%2C%20she%20rinses%20the%20kale%2C%20drizzles%20over%20some%20extra%20virgin%20olive%20oil%2C%20and%20seasons%20with%20salt%2C%20pepper%2C%20lemon%20juice%2C%20and%20chile%20flakes.%20Then%2C%20she%20roasts%20it%20in%20the%20air%20fryer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKale%20roasts%20really%2C%20really%20nice%20and%20gets%20a%20real%20nice%20flavor%20and%20texture%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFish%20dinner%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Salmon%20with%20mashed%20potatoes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65df098890413ab8e1d75953%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESalmon%20with%20mashed%20potatoes.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMorse%20aims%20to%20eat%20at%20least%20two%20portions%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanti-inflammatory-foods-to-help-prevent-chronic-inflammation-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoily%20fish%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20week%20because%20it%20contains%20heart-healthy%20fats%20and%20aids%20brain%20function.%20The%20FDA%20recommends%20adults%20eat%20eight%20ounces%20of%20fish%20or%20seafood%20weekly%2C%20based%20on%20a%202%2C000-calorie%20daily%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20she%20has%20white%20fish%20or%20shrimp%20in%20the%20fridge%2C%20she%20mig