nse%20Of%20Karnataka%20Government's%20Language%20Mandate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fu2uuj24o_kannada-1200-_625x300_29_December_23.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20recent%20decisions%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20have%20garnered%20significant%20national%20attention.%20First%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsouth%2Fbengaluru-60-kannada-kannada-language-row-after-shops-get-60-kannada-order-pro-kannada-groups-go-on-rampage-4750179%5C%22%3E60%25%20of%20all%20signage%20must%20be%20in%20the%20local%20Kannada%20language%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Second%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fshows%2Fthe-southern-view%2Fmncs-in-karnataka-to-display-number-of-kannadigas-employed-on-notice-board-763346%5C%22%3Eall%20multinational%20corporations%3C%2Fa%3E%20(MNCs)%20must%20disclose%20the%20number%20of%20Kannada-speaking%20employees%20in%20their%20offices%2C%20with%20this%20data%20prominently%20displayed%20on%20signboards.%20Failure%20to%20comply%20may%20result%20in%20government%20action.%20The%20latter%20order%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20has%20sparked%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20decisions%20did%20not%20come%20about%20in%20a%20void.%20The%20Kannada%20linguistic%20identity%20holds%20considerable%20sway%20over%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20Kannada-speaking%20populace.%20The%20Congress%20government's%20appeal%20to%20this%20sub-national%20linguistic%20identity%20comes%20just%20months%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20suggesting%20a%20broader%20electoral%20strategy.%20By%20shifting%20focus%20from%20national%20to%20regional%20issues%2C%20the%20Congress%20aims%20to%20replicate%20the%20blueprint%20that%20proved%20successful%20during%20the%202023%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20its%20five%20promises%2C%20the%20party%20localised%20the%20election%20discourse%2C%20resonating%20with%20Karnataka-specific%20concerns.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20underscores%20the%20underlying%20anxieties%20regarding%20jobs%20and%20linguistic%20identity%20among%20Kannada-speaking%20youth%2C%20a%20phenomenon%20not%20unique%20to%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Tool%20For%20Congress%20To%20Counter%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitically%2C%20the%20Kannada%20linguistic%20identity%20serves%20as%20a%20potent%20tool%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20counter%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20(BJP)%20overarching%20pan-India%20narrative.%20While%20the%20BJP%20prioritises%20national%20issues%20such%20as%20the%20Ram%20Temple%2C%20Article%20370%2C%20and%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20the%20Congress%20aims%20to%20leverage%20sub-national%20sentiments.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20the%20Congress%20has%20sought%20to%20foreground%20the%20Kannada%20linguistic%20identity.%20In%202018%2C%20a%20panel%20appointed%20by%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government%2C%20ahead%20of%20state%20assembly%20elections%2C%20recommended%20the%20recognition%20of%20a%20separate%20Karnataka%20state%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20last%20year's%20Amul%20versus%20Nandini%20controversy%2C%20positioned%20by%20the%20Congress%20as%20a%20battle%20to%20protect%20a%20Karnataka-based%20dairy%20brand%2C%20preceded%20the%20assembly%20elections.%20With%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20looming%2C%20the%20recent%20language%20mandate%20signifies%20an%20attempt%20to%20tap%20into%20sub-national%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20language%20mandate%20comes%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20Karnataka's%20dispute%20with%20the%20centre%20over%20tax%20revenues%2C%20wherein%20leaders%20like%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20his%20deputy%20D.K.%20Shivakumar%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20Centre's%20fund%20devolution%2C%20which%20they%20deemed%20unfair.%20Through%20the%20protests%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20government%2C%20along%20with%20their%20counterparts%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Kerala%2C%20alleged%20that%20southern%20states%20have%20not%20been%20given%20their%20rightful%20due.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBanking%20On%20Regional%20Identities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20broader%20level%2C%20looking%20at%20the%20language%20diktat%20alongside%20the%20ongoing%20battle%20over%20revenue%20sharing%2C%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20clear%20attempt%20to%20highlight%20regional%20identities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20Siddaramaiah%20government's%20decision%20suggests%20there%20may%20be%20a%20link%20to%20the%20upcoming%20elections%2C%20the%20step%20is%20likely%20to%20find%20support%20among%20certain%20sections%20of%20the%20Kannada-speaking%20population%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20other%20regions%20of%20the%20state.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-england-union-minister-pralhad-joshi-backs-bengalurus-60-kannada-rule-4753107%5C%22%3EKannada%20linguistic%20identity%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20strong%20support%20base.%20Over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20several%20incidents%20have%20highlighted%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20last%20year%2C%20a%20student%20unfurled%20the%20Karnataka%20flag%20at%20his%20graduation%20ceremony%20in%20the%20UK.%20The%20video%20of%20the%20ceremony%20was%20widely%20shared%20on%20social%20media.%20In%20March%202023%2C%20a%20video%20clip%20of%20an%20argument%20between%20an%20auto%20driver%20and%20a%20passenger%20was%20widely%20circulated%20on%20X.%20The%20driver%20was%20seen%20asking%20passengers%20to%20talk%20in%20Kannada%20and%20refused%20to%20speak%20in%20Hindi.%20The%20video%20sparked%20debates%20around%20regional%20identities%2C%20especially%20in%20cosmopolitan%20cities%20like%20Bengaluru.%20Both%20these%20incidents%20underscored%20the%20extent%20of%20influence%20the%20Kannada%20linguistic%20identity%20has%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%2C%20Congress%20Are%20On%20The%20Same%20Page%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20further%20underscores%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20Kannada%20identity.%20Both%20parties%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20bill%20mandating%20signboards%20to%20use%20at%20least%2060%25%20Kannada.%20BJP%20leaders%20R.%20Ashok%20and%20Suresh%20Kumar%20welcomed%20the%20bill%2C%20arguing%20that%20this%20was%20a%20much-needed%20step%20to%20protect%20Kannada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202023%2C%20when%20the%20K%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsiddaramaiah-karnataka-rakshana-vedike-bbmp-bengaluru-shops-get-60-kannada-order-karnataka-language-row-in-focus-4739519%5C%22%3Eannada%20Rakshana%20Vedike%3C%2Fa%3E%20vandalised%20shops%20and%20establishments%20for%20not%20having%20Kannada%20signboards%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20appeared%20to%20be%20on%20the%20same%20page.%20Both%20parties%20argued%20that%20the%20underlying%20demand%20to%20have%20more%20Kannada%20signboards%20was%20legitimate.%20The%20BJP%20went%20a%20step%20further%20and%20attacked%20the%20Congress%20for%20arresting%20Kannada%20activists%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20vandalism.%20Former%20Chief%20Minister%20Basavaraj%20Bommai%20pinned%20the%20blame%20on%20the%20Congress%20for%20not%20formulating%20a%20policy%20mandating%20Kannada%20signboards.%20After%20the%20recent%20orders%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20government%2C%20the%20BJP%20targeted%20the%20Congress%20for%20nominating%20Ajay%20Maken%2C%20a%20non-Kannadiga%2C%20as%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20from%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELinguistic%20Identity%20Is%20A%20Strong%20Force%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20sub-national%20linguistic%20politics%2C%20Karnataka%20is%20not%20alone.%20Similar%20demands%20to%20'safeguard'%20languages%20and%20give%20preference%20to%20locals%20in%20jobs%20have%20emerged%20in%20other%20states%20too.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20grew%20out%20of%20the%20rising%20discontent%20among%20Marathi-speaking%20working%20class%20in%20Mumbai.%20The%20party%20has%20campaigned%20extensively%20for%20giving%20preference%20to%20locals%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20employment%20opportunities.%20The%20Haryana%20government%20too%2C%20in%202022%2C%20had%20mandated%20reservations%20for%20locals%20in%20private%20jobs%2C%20though%20the%20law%20was%20later%20struck%20down%20by%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncreased%20support%20for%20sub-national%20identities%20is%20common%20in%20cosmopolitan%20regions%20that%20have%20witnessed%20an%20influx%20of%20'non-native'%20migrants.%20In%20places%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20Mumbai%20or%20Gurugram-regions%20that%20have%20seen%20and%20continue%20to%20see%20an%20influx%20of%20people%20from%20various%20parts%20of%20India-demands%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20local%20language%20and%20preferential%20employment%20to%20'locals'%20have%20been%20quite%20vocal.%20Studies%20have%20also%20shown%20that%20nativist%20feelings%20tend%20to%20intensify%20when%20there%20is%20an%20increased%20influx%20of%20non-native%20individuals.%3Cbr%3E%5CnSeveral%20factors%20are%20at%20play%20behind%20the%20Karnataka%20government's%20language%20mandate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepeating%20the%20assembly%20election%20experience%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20has%20been%20the%20prime%20idea.%20The%20move%20also%20reflects%20the%20sentimental%20draw%20of%20the%20Kannada%20linguistic%20identity%20at%20the%20grassroots.%20Within%20Bengaluru%20city%20and%20in%20other%20regions%20of%20the%20state%2C%20there%20is%20a%20significant%20section%20of%20the%20population%20drawn%20towards%20this%20identity.%20This%20is%20why%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20actually%20on%20the%20same%20page%20on%20this%20issue.%20If%20anything%2C%20both%20parties%20are%20trying%20to%20outdo%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20assistant%20professor%20of%20International%20Studies%20at%20FLAME%20University)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709120940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fu2uuj24o_kannada-1200-_625x300_29_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmaking-sense-of-karnataka-governments-language-mandate-5143740%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Given%20the%20emotional%20draw%20of%20the%20Kannada%20linguistic%20identity%20in%20large%20parts%20of%20the%20state%2C%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20actually%20on%20the%20same%20page%20on%20the%20issue.%20If%20anything%2C%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20outdo%20each%20other.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmaking-sense-of-karnataka-governments-language-mandate-5143740%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmaking-sense-of-karnataka-governments-language-mandate-5143740%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmaking-sense-of-karnataka-governments-language-mandate-5143740%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Beyond%20Meat%20plans%20to%20hike%20prices%20and%20sharply%20cut%20costs%20as%20part%20of%20a%20huge%20turnaround%20plan%20to%20fight%20slumping%20sales%20of%20plant-based%20meat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20Beyond%20Meat%20produced%2C%20burger%2C%20meatball%20as%20well%20as%20a%20chicken%20nuggets%20lay%20on%20a%20table%20on%20November%2021%2C%202022%20in%20Miami%2C%20Florida.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65df13cd6080194819fab42a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22