20the%20overall%20impact%20of%20these%20pricing%20changes%20to%20meaningfully%20impact%20margin%20across%20the%20balance%20of%20the%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20change%20in%20strategy%20does%20not%20reflect%20an%20abandonment%20of%20our%20long-sought%20price%20parity%20goal%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20company's%20goal%20of%20making%20plant-based%20meat%20the%20same%20price%20as%20animal%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20said%20that%20as%20well%20as%20restoring%20the%20company's%20margins%2C%20the%20pricing%20action%20aimed%20to%20create%20more%20of%20a%20tiered%20pricing%20system%2C%20with%20higher%20prices%20for%20more%20premium%20products%20like%20its%20upcoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestors.beyondmeat.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fnews-release-details%2Fbeyond-meatr-unveils-its-beyond-iv-platform-fourth-generation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBeyond%20IV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20new%20range%20of%20plant-based%20beef%20and%20burgers%20made%20with%20avocado%20oil%20which%20it%20will%20roll%20out%20at%20US%20retailers%20in%20the%20spring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20products%2C%20including%20those%20in%20grocery%20stores%2C%20would%20barely%20change%20in%20price%2C%20Brown%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECFO%20Lubi%20Kutua%20told%20investors%20that%20Beyond%20Meat%20was%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20confident%26quot%3B%20that%20overall%2C%20the%20changes%20in%20price%20would%20offset%20or%20more%20than%20offset%20the%20expected%20loss%20of%20volume%20caused%20by%20higher%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMisinformation%20about%20plant-based%20meat%20is%20'scaring%20customers%20away'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20Meat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestors.beyondmeat.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fnews-release-details%2Fbeyond-meatr-reports-fourth-quarter-and-full-year-2023-financial%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%3C%2Fa%3E%20net%20revenues%20for%202023%20were%20%24343.4%20million%2C%20a%20decrease%20of%2018%25%20compared%20to%202022.%20US%20sales%20fell%20by%20almost%20a%20third%2C%20whereas%20international%20sales%20rose%20about%2020%25%2C%20mainly%20because%20of%20a%20significant%20jump%20in%20distribution%20to%20restaurants.%20It%20attributed%20declining%20US%20sales%20to%20weak%20demand%20for%20plant-based%20products%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Beyond%20Meat%20offering%20more%20discounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20sales%20of%20Beyond%20Meat's%20products%20to%20the%20food-service%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20which%20includes%20restaurant%20chains%20like%20McDonald's%20and%20Pizza%20Hut%20%E2%80%94%20made%20up%20less%20than%20a%20quarter%20of%20its%20US%20business%2C%20compared%20to%20more%20than%20half%20of%20its%20European%20business.%20Its%20US%20business%20accounted%20for%20around%2060%25%20of%20its%20total%20revenues%2C%20compared%20to%2072.5%25%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20posted%20a%20gross%20loss%20for%20the%20year%20of%20%2482.7%20million%2C%20compared%20to%20a%20loss%20of%20%2423.7%20million%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20said%20that%20Beyond%20Meat%20had%20struggled%20as%20the%20meat%20industry%20tried%20to%20%26quot%3Bpoison%26quot%3B%20the%20plant-based%20industry%20with%20misinformation%20and%20claims%20about%20the%20products%20not%20being%20healthy%2C%20which%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bscaring%20customers%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20broad%20pricing%20programs%20we%20put%20in%20place%20over%20the%20last%2018%20months%20simply%20didn't%20accomplish%20the%20goal%20of%20crossing%20from%20early%20adopters%20into%20the%20mainstream%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20retrospect%2C%20the%20noise%20and%20swirl%20surrounding%20the%20category%20reached%20decibels%20that%20were%20perhaps%20sufficient%20to%20ground%20out%20pricing%20and%20other%20messages.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rounders%20of%20Bosh!%2C%20a%20UK-based%20plant-based%20brand%20that%20makes%20recipe%20books%20and%20sells%20packaged%20products%2C%20t