C%26quot%3B%20Sunil%20Bharti%20Mittal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remain%20committed%20to%20working%20towards%20strengthening%20the%20economic%20and%20bilateral%20trade%20relationships%20between%20our%20two%20great%20nations.%20I%20am%20thankful%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20the%20UK%2C%20whose%20support%20and%20keen%20attention%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20business%20has%20been%20critical%20in%20making%20the%20country%20an%20attractive%20investment%20destination%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunil%20Bharti%20Mittal%20was%20conferred%20with%20Padma%20Bhushan%2C%20India's%20third%20highest%20civilian%20honour%2C%20in%202007.%C2%A0He%20served%20as%20Chair%20of%20the%20B20%20India%20Action%20Council%20on%20African%20Economic%20Integration%20during%20India's%20G20%20Presidency.%20He%20is%20also%20a%20serving%20Commissioner%20at%20the%20International%20Telecommunication%20Union%2FUNESCO%20Broadband%20Commission%20for%20Sustainable%20Development.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnighthood%2C%20the%20Knight%20Commander%20(KBE)%2C%20is%20conferred%20for%20a%20pre-eminent%20contribution%20in%20any%20field%20of%20activity%20(usually%2C%20but%20not%20exclusively%2C%20at%20the%20national%20level)%2C%20or%20in%20a%20capacity%20recognised%20by%20peer%20groups%20as%20inspirational%20and%20significant%20nationally%20and%20demonstrates%20sustained%20commitment.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20KBE%20is%20awarded%20in%20an%20honorary%20capacity%20to%20foreign%20nationals.%20While%20the%20Knighthood%20conferred%20on%20UK%20nationals%20gives%20them%20the%20title%20of%20Sir%20or%20Dame%2C%20non-UK%20nationals%20conferred%20with%20the%20Honour%2C%20add%20KBE%20(or%20DBE%20for%20women)%20after%20their%20name%20instead%20of%20using%20titles%20such%20as%20Sir%20or%20Dame.%20Previous%20recipients%20of%20the%20Honorary%20KBE%20include%20Ratan%20Tata%20(2009)%2C%20Ravi%20Shankar%20(2001)%20and%20Jamshed%20Irani%20(1997).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709119920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-09%2Fsunil-mittal-ndtv_650x400_41506497896.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunil-bharti-mittal-receives-honorary-knighthood-from-king-charles-5143779%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sunil%20Bharti%20Mittal%2C%20the%20Founder%20and%20Chairperson%20of%20Bharti%20Enterprises%2C%20was%20awarded%20the%20Honorary%20Knighthood%20by%20King%20Charles%20III%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%20Mr%20Mittal%20is%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20receive%20a%20Knighthood%20from%20King%20Charles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunil-bharti-mittal-receives-honorary-knighthood-from-king-charles-5143779%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunil-bharti-mittal-receives-honorary-knighthood-from-king-charles-5143779%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunil-bharti-mittal-receives-honorary-knighthood-from-king-charles-5143779%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kim%20Seon%20Ho%20CONFIRMED%20to%20appear%20on%20Eating%20Brothers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709119628000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108074816%2Cimgsize-76886.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fkim-seon-ho-to-appear-on-eating-brothers-season-2-after-three-year-hiatus%2Farticleshow%2F108074793.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108074793.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKim%20Seon%20Ho%20will%20end%20his%20hiatus%20from%20variety%20shows%20with%20a%20guest%20appearance%20on%20'Eating%20Brothers'%20Season%202.%20He%20recently%20concluded%20'The%20Pursuit%20of%20Happyness'%20and%20is%20preparing%20for%20'The%20Tyrant'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%2C%20BJP%20On%20Warpath%20Over%20Minister's%20'China%20Flag%20On%20Indian%20Rocket'%20Ad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20newspaper%20ad%20hailing%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20second%20launch%20pad%20for%20India's%20space%20agency%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fisro%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EISRO%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Kulsekarapatinam%20-%20has%20triggered%20a%20furious%20row%20after%20what%20an%20image%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fchina%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChinese%20flag%3C%2Fa%3E%20figured%20prominently%20on%20the%20rocket%20in%20the%20poster.%20The%20ad%20was%20commissioned%20by%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Animal%20Husbandry%20Minister%20Anitha%20Radhakrishnan%2C%20who%20did%20so%20in%20his%20personal%20capacity%2C%20NDTV%20was%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Radhakrishnan%20has%20been%20unavailable%20for%20comment%2C%20but%20Thoothukudi%20MP%20Kanimozhi%20(in%20whose%20constituency%20the%20ISRO%20facility%20will%20be%20built)%20has%20defended%20her%20party.%20She%20acknowledged%20the%20error%20-%20attributed%20to%20the%20artwork%20designer%20-%20and%20said%20the%20issue%20does%20not%20merit%20the%20backlash%20it%20has%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poster%20itself%20shows%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fpm-modi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20who%20was%20in%20the%20state%2C%20one%20in%20which%20his%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20traditionally%20struggled%20for%20votes%2C%20this%20week%20to%20drum%20up%20support%20before%20the%20general%20election%20-%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20side-by-side%2C%20with%20a%20rocket%20in%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20of%20the%20controversy%20is%20that%20rocket%20-%20its%20red%20nose%20features%20four%20golden%20stars%20arced%20around%20the%20right%20side%20of%20a%20larger%20fifth%20star.%20This%20is%20the%20same%20emblem%20that%20marks%20the%20Chinese%20national%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20been%20quick%20to%20pounce%20on%20the%20error.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20ripped%20into%20the%20ruling%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%2C%20which%20thumped%20the%20BJP%20(then%20allied%20with%20the%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam)%20in%202019%20general%20and%202021%20state%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nadu-news%2Fcrossed-limits-pm-modi-hits-out-at-dmk-over-china-rocket-advertisement-5142662%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BCrossed%20Limits%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Hits%20Out%20At%20DMK%20In%20%26quot%3BChina%20Rocket%26quot%3B%20Ad%20Row%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDMK%20does%20not%20do%20work%20and%20takes%20false%20credit.%20They%20paste%20their%20stickers%20on%20our%20schemes.%20But%20now%20they%20have%20crossed%20the%20limit...%20they%20pasted%20China's%20sticker%20to%20take%20credit%20for%20the%20ISRO%20launchpad...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20accept%20India's%20progress%20in%20the%20space%20sector.%20They%20do%20not%20want%20to%20present%20India's%20space%20success%20to%20the%20world.%20They%20have%20insulted%20our%20scientists%20and%20our%20space%20sector.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-india-gets-its-second-space-port-rocket-startups-excited-5141788%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAs%20India%20Gets%20Its%20Second%20Space%20Port%2C%20Rocket%20Startups%20Excited%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20it%20is%20high%20time%20the%20DMK%20is%20punished%20for%20their%20deeds%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20thundered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Modi's%20sharp%20attacks%20have%20been%20amplified%20by%20the%20BJP's%20state%20unit%20boss%2C%20K%20Annamalai%2C%20who%20posted%20a%20long%20and%20emotive%20post%20on%20X%2C%20in%20which%20he%20slammed%20his%20rival's%20%26quot%3Btotal%20disregard%20for%20our%20country's%20sovereignty%26quot%3B%20and%20labelled%20the%20rocket%20issue%20a%20%26quot%3Bmanifestation%20of%20DMK's%20commitment%20to%20China%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20advertisement%20by%20DMK%20Minister%20Thiru%20Anita%20Radhakrishnan%20to%20leading%20Tamil%20dailies%20today%20is%20a%20manifestation%20of%20DMK's%20commitment%20to%20China%20%26amp%3B%20their%20total%20disregard%20for%20our%20country's%20sovereignty.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDMK%2C%20a%20party%20flighing%20high%20on%20corruption%2C%20has%20been%20desperate%20to%20paste%20stickers%20ever%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fg6CeTzd9TZ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fg6CeTzd9TZ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20K.Annamalai%20(%40annamalai_k)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fannamalai_k%2Fstatus%2F1762716958146146419%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2028%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20a%20day%20when%20the%20PM%20is%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu...%20a%20DMK%20minister%20gives%20out%20a%20newspaper%20ad%20with%20a%20Chinese%20rocket%2C%20and%20Kanimozhi%2C%20a%20senior%20MP%2C%20defends%20it%2C%20saying%2C%20'What%20is%20wrong%20in%20having%20a%20Chinese%20picture%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20MP%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20India%20has%20declared%20China%20an%20'enemy%20country'.%20The%20PM%20invited%20Chinese%20PM%20(Xi%20Jinping)%20and%20they%20went%20to%20Mamallapuram%20(a%20historic%20temple%20town%20near%20Chennai).%20You%20(the%20BJP)%20don't%20want%20to%20accept%20the%20truth%20and%20so%20are%20finding%20reasons%20to%20divert%20the%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDMK%20wants%20to%20stop%20the%20rocket-launching%20facility%20from%20coming%20here.%20And%2C%20for%20that%2C%20they%20are%20going%20to%20any%20end%20to%20please%20their%20(Chinese)%20masters.%20When%20India%20is%20celebrating...%20we%20have%20DMK%20glorifying%20China%2C%20Chinese%20people%2C%20and%20their%20flag.%20We%20expect%20a%20bare%20minimum%20apology...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Annamalai%20ranted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709119620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fn0v9f2q8_china-flag-and-modi-and-stalin_625x300_28_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftamil-nadu-minister-china-flag-isro-rocket-ad-pm-bjp-on-warpath-over-ministers-china-flag-on-indian-rocket-ad-5143747%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20newspaper%20ad%20hailing%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20second%20launch%20pad%20for%20India's%20space%20agency%20ISRO%20-%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Kulsekarapatinam%20-%20has%20triggered%20a%20furious%20row%20after%20what%20an%20image%20of%20the%20Chinese%20flag%20figured%20prominently%20on%20the%20rocket%20in%20the%20poster.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftamil-nadu-minister-china-flag-isro-rocket-ad-pm-bjp-on-warpath-over-ministers-china-flag-on-indian-rocket-ad-5143747%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftamil-nadu-minister-china-flag-isro-rocket-ad-pm-bjp-on-warpath-over-ministers-china-flag-on-indian-rocket-ad-5143747%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftamil-nadu-minister-china-flag-isro-rocket-ad-pm-bjp-on-warpath-over-ministers-china-flag-on-indian-rocket-ad-5143747%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2214-Month%20Wait%2C%20Then%20Strike%3A%20Himachal%20Royals%20Open%20New%20Front%20For%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVirbhadra%20Singh%2C%20Congress's%20tallest%20leader%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20a%20six-time%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20died%20on%20July%208%2C%202021.%20But%20a%20year%20later%2C%20the%20dead%20leader%20was%20still%20the%20key%20face%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20state%20election.%20There%20were%20faultlines%2C%20of%20course.%20The%20Congress%20was%20helmed%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20by%20Virbhadra%20Singh's%20wife%20Pratibha%20Singh%2C%20and%20the%20party's%20campaign%20committee%20was%20headed%20by%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%2C%20a%20grassroots-level%20leader%20and%20a%20known%20critic%20of%20the%20late%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leadership%2C%20however%2C%20managed%20to%20project%20a%20united%20front%20and%20the%20party%20won%2040%20seats%20out%20of%20the%2068%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20ousting%20the%20incumbent%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bigger%20challenge%2C%20however%2C%20was%20waiting.%20Pratibha%20Singh%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20frontrunner%20for%20the%20top%20post%2C%20but%20the%20Congress%20decided%20to%20bet%20on%20Mr%20Sukhu.%20The%20mother-son%20duo%20of%20Pratibha%20Singh%20and%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20swallowed%20defeat.%20Fourteen%20months%20on%2C%20as%20Mr%20Sukhu%20fights%20to%20save%20his%20government%20after%20dramatic%20developments%20during%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20knives%20are%20out.%20The%20discontent%20packed%20away%20for%20another%20time%20has%20re-emerged%2C%20with%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20resigning%20as%20minister%20and%20accusing%20Mr%20Sukhu%20of%20disrespecting%20his%20father%20despite%20the%20Congress%20winning%20the%20polls%20in%20his%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Royal%20Veteran%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20member%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20royal%20family%20of%20Bushahr%2C%20Virbhadra%20Singh%20was%20fondly%20called%20%26quot%3BRaja%20Sahib%26quot%3B.%20An%20alumnus%20of%20the%20prestigious%20Bishop%20Cotton%20School%20in%20Shimla%20and%20Delhi's%20St%20Stephen's%20College%2C%20he%20became%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%201962.%20He%20would%20get%20elected%20to%20the%20Lower%20House%20of%20Parliament%20four%20more%20times.%20Following%20two%20stints%20as%20a%20central%20minister%2C%20he%20became%20Chief%20Minister%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%201983.%20He%20would%20go%20on%20to%20occupy%20the%20post%20six%20times%20during%20his%20long%20political%20career.%20He%20lost%20the%20post%20in%202017%20when%20the%20BJP%20won%20the%20state%20polls%20and%20Jairam%20Thakur%20took%20over%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh's%20last%20years%20on%20the%20political%20landscape%20overlapped%20with%20Mr%20Sukhu's%20tenure%20as%20state%20Congress%20chief%20and%20there%20was%20no%20love%20lost%20between%20them.%20So%20much%20so%20that%20at%20one%20point%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20refused%20to%20share%20stage%20with%20Mr%20Sukhu.%20The%20leadership%20did%20manage%20a%20truce%20but%20the%20acrimony%20remained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Grassroots%20Leader%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20rise%20of%20Mr%20Sukhu%20was%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20that%20of%20Mr%20Singh.%20Coming%20from%20an%20ordinary%20family%2C%20he%20started%20out%20as%20an%20activist%20of%20the%20Congress's%20students%20wing%2C%20NSUI.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20councillor%20in%20Shimla%20municipal%20corporation%20before%20being%20elected%20to%20the%20Himachal%20assembly%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202003.%20A%20four-time%20MLA%2C%20he%20took%20over%20as%20state%20Congress%20chief%20in%202019%2C%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20his%20rivalry%20with%20Virbhadra%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20factor%20was%20that%20the%20Vibhadra%20Singh%20camp%20did%20not%20perform%20very%20well%20in%20the%202022%20polls%2C%20depriving%20them%20of%20the%20political%20muscle%20required%20to%20clinch%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Balancing%20Act%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Mr%20Sukhu%20was%20named%20as%20the%20high%20command's%20Chief%20Minister%20choice%2C%20Pratibha%20Singh%20was%20seen%20to%20be%20the%20frontrunner%20for%20the%20top%20post.%20When%20the%20Congress%20decided%20otherwise%2C%20it%20tried%20a%20balancing%20act%20to%20prevent%20a%20mutiny.%20The%20state%20Congress%20president%20post%20stayed%20with%20Pratibha%20Singh%20and%20her%20son%20Vikramditya%20was%20given%20a%20minister's%20post.%20%26quot%3BWe%20accept%20the%20decision%20taken%20by%20Congress%20high%20command%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20after%20the%20big%20announcement.%20Mr%20Sukhu%20ruled%20out%20any%20discontent%20in%20the%20Congress%20ranks%20following%20his%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Well-Timed%20Strike%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Congress%20struggled%20to%20recover%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20stunner%20pulled%20off%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20royals%20opened%20up%20another%20front.%20In%20a%20press%20conference%20this%20morning%2C%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20accused%20the%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20government%20of%20disrespecting%20his%20father%20and%20ignoring%20the%20voices%20of%20MLAs%20in%20its%2014-month%20rule.%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20resigned%20as%20minister%20and%20said%20that%20the%20ball%20is%20in%20the%20Congress%20leadership's%20court.%20Congress'%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20has%20said%20that%20the%20leadership%20will%20not%20shy%20away%20from%20%26quot%3Bdifficult%20decisions%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIndividuals%20are%20not%20important%2C%20it's%20the%20mandate%20that%20we%20have%20to%20respect.%20All%20options%20are%20open%20and%20the%20party%20is%20supreme.%20We%20will%20take%20whatever%20decision%20is%20required%20and%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709119320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F2inmvl7_virbhadra-sukhu-split_625x300_28_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsukhvinder-singh-sukhu-himachal-congress-virbhadra-singh-14-month-wait-then-strike-himachal-royals-open-new-front-for-congress-5143207%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virbhadra%20Singh%2C%20Congress's%20tallest%20leader%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20a%20six-time%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20breathed%20his%20last%20on%20July%208%2C%202021.%20But%20Congress%20fought%20state%20polls%20a%20year%20a%20later%20not%20in%20the%20name%20of%20any%20living%20leader%2C%20but%20in%20the%20name%20of%20its%20dead%20veteran%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsukhvinder-singh-sukhu-himachal-congress-virbhadra-singh-14-month-wait-then-strike-himachal-royals-open-new-front-for-congress-5143207%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsukhvinder-singh-sukhu-himachal-congress-virbhadra-singh-14-month-wait-then-strike-himachal-royals-open-new-front-for-congress-5143207%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsukhvinder-singh-sukhu-himachal-congress-virbhadra-singh-14-month-wait-then-strike-himachal-royals-open-new-front-for-congress-5143207%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Emraan%20reveals%20Bhatt%20Saab%20wanted%20him%20out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709119256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F