t%3D%5C%22389%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty.%20Photo%3A%20Intifada%20P.%20Basheer%20and%20Azam%20Abbas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20have%20since%20been%20questions%20over%20the%20authorisation%20granted%20for%20operating%20the%20fireworks%20factory%20in%20Magardha%20Road%2C%20a%20densely%20populated%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E39%20houses%20completely%20destroyed%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpread%20across%201.75%20acres%2C%20the%20factory%2C%20owned%20by%20Raju%20Agrawal%2C%20Somesh%20Agrawal%2C%20and%20Pradeep%20Agrawal%2C%20had%20explosives%20stored%20in%20two%20separate%20godowns.%20Electrical%20wiring%20ran%20through%20the%20factory%2C%20leading%20to%20speculation%20of%20a%20possible%20short%20circuit%20igniting%20the%20blaze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20blast%20damaged%2059%20nearby%20houses%2C%20with%2039%20completely%20destroyed.%20Of%20this%2039%20were%2021%20constructed%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana.%20Many%20of%20those%20who%20lived%20closest%20to%20the%20factory%20also%20worked%20in%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20explosions%20were%20so%20intense%20that%20debris%20scattered%20far%20and%20wide%2C%20with%20fragments%20landing%20up%20to%2070%20metres%20away.%20The%20force%20of%20the%20blasts%20was%20felt%20within%20a%2015-kilometre%20radius%2C%20shattering%20windows%20of%20homes%20situated%20approximately%205%20kilometres%20away%20on%20Indore%20Road%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBharati%20Raju%20Kamedia%2C%20the%20municipal%20president%2C%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20area%20was%20previously%20labelled%20as%20%E2%80%98rural%E2%80%99%2C%20allowing%20the%20factory%20to%20operate%20for%20two%20decades%20before%20being%20incorporated%20into%20the%20ward%20following%20boundary%20changes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKamedia%20said%20that%20the%20factory%2C%20situated%20in%20the%20Bairagarh%20ward%2C%20is%20surrounded%20by%20residential%20houses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHarda%20collector%20Aditya%20Singh%20said%20that%20the%2039%20houses%20that%20have%20been%20decimated%20are%20within%20a%20100-metre%20radius.%20%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20is%20actively%20assessing%20dwellings%20within%20an%20extra%20500-metre%20range%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20claimed%20there%20has%20been%20swift%20response%20and%20immediate%20relief%20totalling%20Rs%205%20lakhs%20has%20been%20disbursed%20to%20all%20affected%20families.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20assets%20of%20the%20perpetrators%20have%20been%20seized%20for%20restitution%20purposes%20%E2%80%9CAll%20materials%20recovered%20from%20the%20site%20have%20been%20seized%20by%20the%20district%20authorities%20for%20further%20investigation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeized%20property%20includes%20their%20agricultural%20land%2C%20house%2C%20and%20shop%20which%20total%20an%20estimated%20value%20of%20Rs%2018%20crore.%20The%20seized%20property%20will%20be%20auctioned%2C%20and%20the%20proceeds%20will%20be%20used%20to%20provide%20relief%20to%20the%20victims.%20The%20district%20administration%20has%20also%20seized%20assets%20in%20other%20locations%20belonging%20to%20the%20accused%2C%20and%20is%20collecting%20information%20about%20properties%20owned%20by%20their%20relatives.%20This%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20in%20compliance%20with%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%2C%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20said%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Eone%20woman%20has%20suffered%20an%20amputation%2C%20with%2031%20individuals%20sustaining%20partial%20fractures%2C%20ten%20of%20whom%20remain%20hospitalised%20in%20Bhopal%20and%20Indore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20far%2C%20seven%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%2C%20with%2020%20licences%2C%20including%20those%20of%2016%20from%20the%20accused%E2%80%99s%20kin%2C%20and%20four%20others%2C%20suspended.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28164259%2FCamera-01-1024x576.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28164259%2FCamera-01-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28164259%2FCamera-01-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28164259%2FCamera-01.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699321%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFamilies%20of%20those%20killed%20in%20the%20Harda%20firecracker%20blast%20at%20the%20sit-in%20protest.%20Photo%3A%20Akansha%20Deshmukh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESeveral%20%E2%80%98irregularities%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20factory%20in%20Bairagarh%20covered%20an%20area%20of%202.5%20acres%2C%20but%20according%20to%20official%20records%2C%20only%203%2C500%20square%20feet%20was%20diverted%20for%20other%20use.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20there%20permanent%20constructions%20occupy%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20say%20protesters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20action%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20authorities%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202022%20during%20an%20investigation%20by%20the%20then%20SDM%20of%20Harda%2C%20Shruti%20Aggarwal%2C%20several%20irregularities%20were%20revealed%2C%20including%20the%20fact%20that%C2%A0%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Epproved%20plans%20or%20drawings%20of%20the%20factory%20were%20missing%2C%20that%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20factory%20was%20a%20three-storey%20building%20instead%20of%20a%20single%20storey%2C%20with%20different%20operations%20on%20each%20floor%2C%20that%20t%3C%2Fspan%3Ehe%20factory%E2%80%99s%20godown%20was%20inside%20the%20building%2C%20contrary%20to%20regulations%20and%20that%20the%20quantity%20of%20explosives%20exceeded%20the%20licensed%20amount%20by%20a%20large%20margin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMohit%20Chauhan%20(19)%2C%20a%20factory%20worker%2C%20said%20he%20was%20on%20the%20first%20floor%20when%20the%20explosion%20occurred.%20Chauhan%20said%20that%20gunpowder%20was%20also%20stored%20in%20his%20house%2C%20adjacent%20to%20the%20factory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdmitted%20to%20the%20district%20hospital%2C%20Shivdas%20(26)%20said%20he%20was%20working%20at%20the%20warehouse%20adjacent%20to%20Chauhan%E2%80%99s%20house.%20Shivdas%20believes%20that%20a%20box%20of%20gunpowder%20fell%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20explosion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20Anup%20Prajapati%2C%20employed%20in%20the%20fireworks%20factory%2C%20said%20that%20although%20he%20managed%20to%20escape%2C%20his%20uncle%20Priyanshu%2C%20who%20had%20arrived%20to%20check%20on%20him%2C%20on%20learning%20of%20the%20explosion%2C%20succumbed%20to%20fatal%20injuries%20when%20the%20second%20explosion%20occurred.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20employee%2C%20Muskan%20Koghe%2C%20said%20she%20had%20taken%20her%20three-year-old%20daughter%20Pari%20to%20work%20that%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESurvivors%E2%80%99%20demands%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Twenty%20days%20since%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20lives%20of%20those%20affected%20remain%20in%20disarray%2C%20with%20129%20individuals%20from%2048%20families%20still%20residing%20in%20the%20relief%20camp.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAshik%20Ali%20and%20Saina%20are%20a%20couple%20who%20worked%20at%20this%20factory.%20Saina%20said%20that%20chemicals%20were%20stored%20on%20the%20third%20floor%2C%20where%20firecrackers%20were%20made%20and%20coloured%20before%20being%20dried%20and%20packed.%20Ashiq%20Ali%20explained%20that%20they%20used%20a%20flour%20mill%20to%20grind%20chemical%20powder%2C%20and%20they%20were%20unsure%20about%20the%20quantity%20of%20gunpowder%20coming%20in%20and%20going%20out%20of%20the%20factory.%20Workers%20were%20paid%20Rs%20250%20for%20making%201%2C000%20firecrackers.%20Asif%20and%20Saina%20made%204%2C000%20firecrackers%20daily%2C%20earning%20Rs%20500%20each.%20On%20average%2C%20500%20people%20worked%20daily%20in%20this%20factory%2C%20while%202000%20labourers%20worked%20at%20the%20Agarwals%E2%80%99%20four%20other%20factories.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKin%20of%20the%20deceased%20have%20said%20that%20the%20administration%E2%80%99s%20offer%20of%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%20as%20compensation%20is%20inadequate%20for%20rebuilding%20homes%20ravaged%20by%20the%20tragedy.%20Affected%20individuals%20insist%20on%20fair%20compensation%20or%20the%20reconstruction%20of%20their%20houses%20so%20they%20can%20be%20restored%20to%20pre-blast%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProtesters%E2%80%99%20discussions%20with%20officials%2C%20including%20those%20from%20the%20Mandi%20Traders%20Association%2C%20have%20yielded%20little%20progress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20past%2020%20days%2C%20survivors%20and%20their%20families%20have%20been%20housed%20in%20a%20relief%20camp%20at%20the%20ITI%20College%20in%20the%20city.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20demands%20of%20the%20victims%20include%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3ERs%2015%20lakh%20as%20compensation%20to%20the%20families%20of%20the%20deceased%20and%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20to%20the%20injured.%20They%20have%20only%20received%20Rs%205%20lakh%20as%20compensation%20so%20far.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Ensuring%20that%20those%20whose%20houses%20have%20been%20damaged%20receive%20funds%20at%20market%20rates%20to%20rebuild%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3ERs%202.5%20lakh%20to%20compensate%20for%20the%20losses%20suffered%20by%20tenants.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Employment%20opportunities%20for%20the%20disabled%20and%20dependents%20of%20the%20deceased%20workers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EDeployment%20of%20a%20special%20team%20to%20ascertain%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20casualties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESurvivors%20and%20the%20victims%E2%80%99%20families%20have%20demanded%20that%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20incident%20entail%20assessing%20the%20explosion%E2%80%99s%20intensity%20and%20conducting%20forensic%20analysis%20in%20an%20independent%20laboratory.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELegal%20action%2C%20they%20said%2C%20should%20include%20adding%20sections%20of%20murder%2C%20including%20the%20National%20Security%20Act%20(NSA)%20and%20child%20labour%20laws%2C%20to%20the%20cases%20against%20the%20factory%20owner%20Rajesh%20Aggarwal%20and%20the%20other%20accused%2C%20as%20well%20as%20identifying%20responsible%20administrative%20officers%20and%20pressing%20criminal%20charges%20against%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Additionally%2C%20the%20survivors%20and%20kin%20of%20the%20deceased%20said%20that%20a%20separate%20case%20should%20be%20filed%20against%20administrative%20officials%20who%20failed%20to%20take%20appropriate%20action.%20Further%20action%20should%20involve%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20and%20a%20fact-finding%20committee%20chaired%20by%20a%20retired%20high%20court%20judge%2C%20with%20representation%20from%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709119241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F