%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Mr%20Mahajan%20said%20that%20apart%20from%20the%20six%20Congress%20MLAs%20that%20cross-voted%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20at%20least%20ten%20more%20legislators%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20him%20and%20are%20likely%20to%20make%20the%20switch%20to%20the%20BJP%20soon.%20For%20the%20Congress%2C%20Mr%20Mahajan's%20remarks%20will%20sting%20even%20more%20because%20he%20was%20a%20long-time%20member%20of%20the%20party%20and%20had%20quit%20just%20ahead%20of%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFighting%20an%20uphill%20battle%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%20in%20the%20state%20on%20Tuesday%20despite%20having%20just%2025%20MLAs%20in%20the%2068-member%20Assembly%2C%20against%20the%20Congress'%2040.%20It%20was%20helped%20by%20a%20draw%20of%20lots%20going%20in%20its%20favour%20after%20a%20tie.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttributing%20his%20victory%20to%20the%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20government's%20performance%20in%20the%20state%20and%20the%20people%20and%20legislators'%20%26quot%3Bannoyance%26quot%3B%20with%20it%2C%20Mr%20Mahajan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20Himachal%20politics%20for%2045%20years.%20I%20was%20in%20the%20Congress%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20about%20three%20years%20ago.%20So%20I%20know%20people%20from%20both%20parties%20very%20well.%20The%20discontentment%20among%20the%20Congress%20MLAs%20gave%20me%20a%20reason%20to%20speak%20to%20them%20and%20I%20am%20grateful%20to%20them%20for%20supporting%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20resignation%20as%20minister%20of%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%2C%20son%20of%20late%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Virbhadra%20Singh%2C%20Mr%20Mahajan%20-%20who%20was%20known%20to%20be%20close%20to%20the%20leader%20-%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20so%20much%20discontentment%2C%20and%20the%20final%20outcome%20will%20be%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20government%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20Decisions%20like%20the%20Speaker%20suspending%20BJP%20MLAs%20are%20delay%20tactics.%20The%20final%20outcome%2C%20which%20will%20come%20very%20soon%2C%20will%20be%20the%20fall%20of%20this%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20six%20Congress%20MLAs%20and%20three%20Independents%20had%20voted%20for%20him%2C%20Mr%20Mahajan%20claimed%20he%20is%20in%20touch%20with%20at%20least%2010%20more%20legislators%20from%20the%20party%20who%20are%20willing%20to%20join%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20the%20Congress%20Rajya%20Sabha%20candidate%2C%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20being%20an%20'outsider'%20played%20a%20role%20in%20his%20victory%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20every%20MLA%20closely%20and%20I%20have%20groomed%20many%20of%20them.%20The%20fact%20that%20I%20am%20a%20son%20of%20the%20soil%20helped%20me.%20I%20think%20the%20people%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20put%20the%20pressure%20on%20the%20MLAs%20that%20they%20needed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20the%20Congress%20sending%20crisis%20managers%20like%20Karnataka%20Deputy%20Chief%20%C2%A0Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%20and%20former%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%20will%20help%2C%20Mr%20Mahajan%20pointed%20to%20factionalism%20within%20the%20party%20and%20said%20there%20are%20many%20contenders%20for%20the%20chief%20minister's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sharp%20attack%20on%20his%20former%20party%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20(the%20leaders'%20intervention)%20is%20not%20going%20to%20work.%20The%20Congress%20party%20has%20been%20dismantled%20from%20the%20Centre%20to%20the%20states.%20Everybody%20has%20faith%20in%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20JP%20Nadda.%20The%20Congress%20is%20a%20gone%20case%20now.%20I%20think%20it%20is%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20end%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20states%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mahajan%20said%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20last%20month%20has%20also%20helped%20the%20BJP%20in%20Himachal%2C%20which%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20a%20%26quot%3B98%25%20Hindu%20state%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709118780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fjihutjf_harsh-mahajan_625x300_28_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-gone-case-himachal-government-will-fall-soon-bjps-rajya-sabha-winner-5143643%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Riding%20high%20on%20his%20and%20his%20party's%20stunning%20victory%20in%20the%20lone%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20BJP%20leader%20Harsh%20Mahajan%20has%20declared%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bgone%20case%26quot%3B%20and%20its%20government%20in%20the%20state%20will%20%26quot%3Bfall%20very%20soon%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-gone-case-himachal-government-will-fall-soon-bjps-rajya-sabha-winner-5143643%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-gone-case-himachal-government-will-fall-soon-bjps-rajya-sabha-winner-5143643%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-gone-case-himachal-government-will-fall-soon-bjps-rajya-sabha-winner-5143643%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paris%20Olympics%20security%20plans%20stolen%20from%20train%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709118763000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108074457%2Cimgsize-1671597.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fparis-olympics-security-plans-stolen-from-train%2Farticleshow%2F108074