%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Decongestion%20directives%20showing%20result%20in%20Mumbai%3A%20Govt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709116515000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108072836%2Cimgsize-33630.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fdecongestion-directives-showing-result-in-mumbai-more-on-time-flights-now-govt%2Farticleshow%2F108072757.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20aviation%20ministry's%20directives%20to%20reduce%20flights%20at%20Mumbai's%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20International%20Airport%20(CSMIA)%20have%20improved%20air%20traffic.%20Excessive%20slot%20allocation%20and%20poor%20adherence%20caused%20congestion%2C%20but%20restrictions%20on%20non-scheduled%20flights%20during%20peak%20hours%20mitigated%20the%20problem.%2057%25%20of%20flights%20now%20arrive%20on%20time.%20Given%20the%20fact%20that%20Mumbai%20Airport%20has%20severe%20infra%20constraints%20and%20had%20given%20way%20more%20slots%20than%20it%20should%20have%2C%20flights%20not%20adhering%20to%20schedule%20add%20to%20the%20problem%20of%20delayed%20arrivals%20and%20departures.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SAURABH%20SINHA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fdecongestion-directives-showing-result-in-mumbai-more-on-time-flights-now-govt%2Farticleshow%2F108072757.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI%20Action%20On%20Paytm%20Not%20Impacting%20Merchants'%20Trust%2C%20Says%20Survey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20crippling%20restrictions%20imposed%20by%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20on%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20(PPBL)%20are%20not%20impacting%20merchants'%20trust%20in%20the%20payment%20platform%2C%20a%20survey%20has%20said.%20Gurugram-based%20business%20consulting%20and%20services%20company%20Datum%20Intelligence%20said%2059%20per%20cent%20of%20merchants%20continue%20to%20use%20Paytm%20and%20see%20no%20immediate%20impact%20from%20the%20government's%20clampdown.%20The%20company%20surveyed%202%2C000%20merchants%20who%20are%20using%20Paytm%20applications%20for%20accepting%20payments%20across%2012%20cities.%20It%20was%20carried%20out%20between%20February%207%20and%2015%2C%20Datum%20Intelligence%20said%20in%20a%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20showed%20that%2021%20per%20cent%20merchants%20are%20waiting%20for%20more%20information%20and%20only%2013%20per%20cent%20are%20switching%20to%20other%20payment%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDatum%20survey%20also%20found%20that%2076%20per%20cent%20of%20merchants%20use%20Paytm%20for%20accepting%20payments%2C%20followed%20by%2041%20per%20cent%20for%20PhonePe%2C%2033%20per%20cent%20for%20Google%20Pay%20and%2018%20per%20cent%20BharatPe.%20Paytm%20is%20the%20preferred%20app%20for%2058%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20merchants%20surveyed%20followed%20by%2023%20per%20cent%20for%20PhonePe%2C%2012%20per%20cent%20for%20Google%20Pay%20and%20three%20per%20cent%20for%20BharatPe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20behind%20merchants'%20confidence%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20Paytm%20representative%20reached%20out%20to%20them%20after%20the%20RBI%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B71%20per%20cent%20of%20merchants%20are%20feeling%20confident%20to%20continue%20using%20Paytm%20for%20payments%20after%20a%20reach%20out%20by%20a%20Paytm%20representative.%20Only%2011%20per%20cent%20are%20less%20confident%20about%20using%20Paytm%20for%20payments%20and%20around%2014%20per%20cent%20are%20still%20looking%20for%20more%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Datum%20Intelligence%20survey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOverall%2C%20the%20impact%20is%20limited%20on%20the%20merchant%20business%20and%20Paytm%20is%20engaging%20with%20merchants%20to%20reduce%20the%20damage%20and%20merchants%20are%20also%20waiting%20before%20deciding%20on%20alternatives%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20announced%20the%20clampdown%20on%20January%2031%2C%20when%20it%20asked%20PPBL%20-%20an%20associate%20of%20One%2097%20Communications%20-%20to%20stop%20accepting%20new%20deposits%20in%20its%20accounts%20and%20its%20digital%20wallets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20later%20gave%20a%2015-day%20extension%20(till%20March%2015%2C%202024)%20for%20most%20activities%20linked%20to%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank.%20It%20also%20clarified%20that%20customers%20using%20%40paytm%20UPI%20handles%20can%20be%20migrated%20to%20banks%20post%20approval%20from%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709116380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fjppg4f5_paytm_625x300_09_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frbi-action-on-paytm-not-impacting-merchants-trust-says-survey-5143526%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20reason%20behind%20merchants'%20confidence%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20Paytm%20representative%20reached%20out%20to%20them%20after%20the%20RBI%20decision.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frbi-action-on-paytm-not-impacting-merchants-trust-says-survey-5143526%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frbi-action-on-paytm-not-impacting-merchants-trust-says-survey-5143526%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frbi-action-on-paytm-not-impacting-merchants-trust-says-survey-5143526%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ITV%20and%20PBS%E2%80%99%20Greenlight%20Fourth%20Season%20of%20Eagle%20Eye%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Professor%20T%2C%E2%80%99%20Toplining%20Ben%20Miller%2C%20Sold%20by%20Beta%20Film%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A17