ls-how-bjp-leaders-falsely-projected-congress-others-as-pro-pakistan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20retweeted%20a%20post%20claiming%20that%20'Pakistan%20Zindabad'%20slogans%20were%20raised%20in%20the%20the%20Karnataka%20state%20assembly%20after%20re-election%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Dr%20Syed%20Naseer%20Hussain%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20polls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkarnataka-rs-polls-how-bjp-leaders-falsely-projected-congress-others-as-pro-pakistan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22HawkEye%20Founder%20Provides%20Explanation%20Over%20Root's%20LBW%20Row%20In%20Ranchi%20Test%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20massive%20controversy%20surrounding%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Joe%20Root%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1433-joe-root-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJoe%20Root%3C%2Fa%3E's%20LBW%20dismissal%20during%20the%20fourth%20Test%20match%20against%20India%20in%20Ranchi%20with%20several%20ex-cricketers%20even%20criticising%20the%20technology%20for%20what%20they%20thought%20was%20a%20erroneous%20DRS%20review.%20During%20England's%20second%20innings%2C%20Ashwin's%20delivery%20crashed%20into%20Root's%20pads%20but%20the%20umpire%20was%20not%20convinced%20about%20the%20LBW%20shout.%20India%20went%20for%20a%20review%20and%20the%20replay%20showed%20that%20although%20it%20seemed%20like%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20ball%20pitched%20outside%20the%20leg-stump%2C%20the%20technology%20deemed%20it%20fair%20and%20gave%20it%20out.%20Some%20experts%20and%20fans%20were%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20decision%20but%20Paul%20Hawkins%2C%C2%A0the%20founder%20of%20HawkEye%2C%20provided%20an%20explanation%20regarding%20the%20controversial%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20Simon%20Hughes%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftheanalyst%2Fstatus%2F1762480851592331513%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98The%20Analyst'%20podcast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Hawkins%20explained%20the%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20firstly%2C%20you%20measure%20the%20width%20of%20the%20stumps%20on%20each%20day.%20So%20that%20then%20becomes%20the%20line%20between%20what's%20pitched%20in%20line%20and%20what's%20not%20pitched%20in%20line.%20And%20it%20was%20a%20very%20close%20one.%20It's%20one%20that%20in%20tennis%2C%20you%20will%20occasionally%20get%20a%200%20or%200%20scenario%20and%20tennis%20have%20decided%20that%20it's%20not%20out%20until%20it's%20not%200.%20Mm%2C%20it's%201.%20So%20actually%2C%20in%20tennis%2C%20we%20shift%20the%20bounce%20mark%20just%20for%20a%20presentation%20perspective.%20So%20a%200%20becomes%20a%201%2C%20so%20you%20can%20clearly%20see%20the%20mark.%20But%20that's%20just%20a%20presentation%20thing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hawkins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere's%20nothing%20different%20with%20the%20tracking%20or%20the%20answer.%20It%20just%20makes%20it%20clearer%20to%20the%20viewer.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20clearer%20on%20TV%20if%20the%20track%20had%20come%20off%20the%20ball.%20So%20you%20can%20see%20the%20ball%20more%20clearly%20over%20the%20line%2C%20which%20happens%20automatically%20if%20the%20ball%20has%20pitched%20outside%20leg%20stump%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%C2%A0India%20consolidated%20their%20second%20spot%20in%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC)%20standing%20following%20their%20five-wicket%20win%20against%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ben%20Stokes%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1434-ben-stokes-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBen%20Stokes%3C%2Fa%3E'%20England%20in%20the%20fourth%20Test%20at%20Ranchi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hosts%2C%20led%20by%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20took%20an%20unassailable%203-1%20lead%20in%20the%20five-Test%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20point-percentage%20jumped%20from%2059.52%20to%2064.58%20following%20the%20hard-fought%20win%20and%20they%20further%20extended%20the%20gap%20with%20Australia%20(55%25)%20and%20Bangladesh%20(50%25)%2C%20third%20third%20and%20fourth-placed%20teams%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngland%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20are%20languishing%20at%20eighth%20with%2019.44%25%2C%20just%20a%20spot%20ahead%20of%20bottom-placed%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20who%20are%20yet%20to%20open%20their%20account.%20India%20have%20so%20far%20played%20eight%20Tests%20in%20the%20current%C2%A0WTC%C2%A0cycle%2C%20winning%20five%2C%20losing%20two%20and%20drawing%20one%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709116080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fuq929fd8_sad_625x300_28_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fhawkeye-founder-provides-explanation-over-joe-roots-lbw-controversy-in-ranchi-test-5143484%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20was%20a%20massive%20controversy%20surrounding%20Joe%20Root's%20LBW%20dismissal%20during%20the%20fourth%20Test%20match%20against%20India%20in%20Ranchi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Law%20Panel%20May%20Seek%20Simultaneous%20Polls%20In%202029%2C%20Add%20Chapter%20In%20Constitution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Law%20Commission%20is%20likely%20to%20recommend%20adding%20a%20new%20chapter%20to%20the%20Constitution%20on%20'one%20nation%2C%20one%20election'%20and%20holding%20the%20gigantic%20democratic%20exercise%20of%20simultaneous%20polls%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20state%20assemblies%20and%20local%20bodies%20across%20the%20country%20by%20mid-2029%2C%20sources%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%2C%20under%20Justice%20(retd)%20Ritu%20Raj%20Awasthi%2C%20would%20recommend%20an%20amendment%20to%20the%20Constitution%20to%20add%20the%20%26quot%3Bnew%20chapter%20or%20part%26quot%3B%20on%20simultaneous%20elections%2C%20the%20sources%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20would%20also%20recommend%20synchronising%20the%20terms%20of%20legislative%20assemblies%20in%20%26quot%3Bthree%20phases%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years%20so%20that%20the%20first%20simultaneous%20polls%20could%20be%20held%20in%20May-June%202029%20when%20elections%20for%20the%2019th%20Lok%20Sabha%20are%20due.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20chapter%20in%20the%20Constitution%20would%20include%20issues%20related%20to%20%26quot%3Bsimultaneous%20election%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Bsustainability%20of%20simultaneous%20elections%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcommon%20electoral%20roll%26quot%3B%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20state%20legislative%20assemblies%2C%20panchayats%20and%20municipalities%20so%20that%20the%20three-tier%20simultaneous%20polls%20could%20be%20held%20together%20%26quot%3Bin%20one%20go%26quot%3B%2C%20they%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20chapter%20being%20recommended%20will%20have%20power%20of%20non-extant%26quot%3B%20to%20override%20other%20provisions%20in%20the%20Constitution%20dealing%20with%20terms%20of%20assemblies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five-year%20period%20in%20which%20the%20terms%20of%20assemblies%20will%20be%20synchronised%20will%20be%20spread%20over%20three%20phases.%20The%20Commission%20would%20recommend%20that%20the%20first%20phase%20may%20deal%20with%20state%20assemblies%20whose%20period%20will%20have%20to%20be%20curtailed%20by%20a%20few%20months%20--%20three%20or%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20a%20government%20falls%20due%20to%20no%20confidence%20or%20if%20there%20is%20a%20hung%20House%2C%20the%20Commission%20would%20recommend%20constitution%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bunity%20government%26quot%3B%20with%20representatives%20from%20various%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20the%20unity%20government%20formula%20does%20not%20work%2C%20the%20law%20panel%20would%20recommend%20holding%20fresh%20elections%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20term%20of%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuppose%20fresh%20elections%20are%20called%20for%20and%20the%20government%20still%20has%20three%20years%2C%20then%20polls%20should%20be%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20term%20--%20three%20years%20--%20to%20ensure%20sustainability%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20Law%20Commission%2C%20a%20high-level%20committee%20under%20former%20president%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20is%20also%20working%20on%20a%20report%20on%20how%20simultaneous%20polls%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20state%20legislative%20assemblies%2C%20municipalities%20and%20panchayats%20can%20be%20held%20by%20tweaking%20the%20Constitution%20and%20the%20existing%20legal%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20expected%20in%20April-May%20this%20year%2C%20elections%20for%20at%20least%20five%20assemblies%20are%20likely%20to%20take%20place%2C%20while%20state%20polls%20for%20Maharashtra%2C%20Haryana%20and%20Jharkhand%20are%20expected%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20and%20Delhi%20are%20scheduled%20for%20assembly%20polls%20next%20year%2C%20while%20Assam%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Puducherry%20and%20Kerala%20are%20scheduled%20for%202026%2C%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Punjab%20and%20Manipur%20in%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%20nine%20states%20may%20have%20assembly%20polls%20scheduled%20for%202028%20--%20Tripura%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20Nagaland%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Mizoram%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Telangana.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20