uploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08091601%2Fartificial-intelligence-2167835_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EArtificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20has%20immense%20potential%20to%20enhance%20human%20capabilities%20and%20drive%20growth%20in%20several%20industries.%20It%20is%20projected%20to%20greatly%20improve%20governance%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20education%20outcomes.%20However%2C%20this%20potential%20may%20not%20be%20realised%20if%20the%20building%20blocks%20of%20AI%20remain%20concentrated%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20few%20dominant%20companies%20or%20the%20countries%20in%20which%20they%20are%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20priorities%20for%20AI%20adoption%20in%20India%20can%20be%20quite%20different.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penguin.co.in%2Fbook%2Fin-service-of-the-republic%2F%5C%22%3EVijay%20Kelkar%20and%20Ajay%20Shah%20propose%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20toughest%20challenges%20for%20a%20state%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20the%20tax%20system%20%E2%80%93%20involve%20processes%20that%20feature%20a%20high%20number%20of%20transactions%2C%20the%20need%20for%20discretion%2C%20high%20stakes%20for%20individuals%2C%20and%20some%20degree%20of%20secrecy.%20AI%20adoption%20could%20reduce%20the%20complexity%20of%20such%20challenges%20on%20some%20of%20these%20dimensions%2C%20such%20as%20the%20transaction%20volume%20and%20discretion.%20This%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20overcome%20state%20capacity%20limitations%20and%20deliver%20better%20governance%20and%20public%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20widespread%20AI%20adoption%20could%20also%20negatively%20affect%20the%20availability%20of%20low-skilled%20jobs%20upon%20which%20a%20large%20part%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20labour%20force%20depends.%20Thus%2C%20the%20opportunities%20and%20challenges%20for%20India%20might%20be%20significantly%20different%20from%20those%20of%20developed%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnology%20and%20geopolitics%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20intertwined.%20Many%20countries%20have%20identified%20critical%20and%20emerging%20technologies%20that%20are%20essential%20for%20national%20security%20and%20economic%20growth.%20AI%20features%20on%20the%20lists%20of%20all%20countries%20that%20have%20made%20such%20declarations%2C%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftrumpwhitehouse.archives.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2FNational-Strategy-for-CET.pdf%5C%22%3EUnited%20States%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fpublications%2Fthe-uk-as-a-science-and-technology-superpower%2Fthe-uk-as-a-science-and-technology-superpower-accessible-html-version-of-letter%5C%22%3EUnited%20Kingdom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdefence-industry-space.ec.europa.eu%2Fsystem%2Ffiles%2F2023-10%2FC_2023_6689_1_EN_annexe_acte_autonome_part1_v9.pdf%5C%22%3EEuropean%20Union%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.industry.gov.au%2Fpublications%2Flist-critical-technologies-national-interest%5C%22%3EAustralia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.europarl.europa.eu%2FRegData%2Fetudes%2FATAG%2F2023%2F751417%2FEPRS_ATA(2023)751417_EN.pdf%5C%22%3EJapan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20technologies%20are%20not%20just%20an%20area%20of%20focus%20but%20also%20of%20strategic%20interest.%20For%20instance%2C%20US%20policymakers%20are%20operationalising%20the%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fspeeches-remarks%2F2022%2F10%2F13%2Fremarks-by-national-security-advisor-jake-sullivan-on-the-biden-harris-administrations-national-security-strategy%2F%5C%22%3Ea%20small%20yard%20with%20a%20high%20fence%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20for%20critical%20technologies%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20keeping%20the%20chokepoints%20for%20foundational%20technologies%20under%20US%20control.%20From%20their%20longstanding%20approach%20of%20staying%20a%20few%20generations%20ahead%20of%20rivals%20in%20critical%20technologies%2C%20the%20American%20focus%20is%20now%20to%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fspeeches-remarks%2F2022%2F09%2F16%2Fremarks-by-national-security-advisor-jake-sullivan-at-the-special-competitive-studies-project-global-emerging-technologies-summit%2F%5C%22%3Emaintain%20as%20large%20of%20a%20lead%20as%20possible%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20these%20considerations%2C%20for%20India%20to%20pursue%20its%20national%20interests%2C%20it%20will%20have%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20maintain%20strategic%20autonomy%20with%20respect%20to%20this%20critical%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EInputs%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20of%20AI%20systems%20requires%20different%20inputs%3A%20data%2C%20computation%2C%20models%2C%20and%20applications.%20These%20inputs%20can%20be%20visualized%20as%20layers%2C%20with%20data%20and%20computation%20contributing%20to%20the%20model%2C%20which%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20supports%20the%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28150030%2Fimage-1879.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22818%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28150030%2Fimage-1879.png%20607w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28150030%2Fimage-1879-300x246.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699309%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22670%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFigure%201%3A%20The%20components%20of%20the%20AI%20supply%20chain%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompanies%20involved%20in%20developing%20AI%20models%20or%20applications%20face%20entry%20barriers%20at%20each%20of%20these%20stages.%20It%20is%20not%20uncommon%20for%20a%20single%20company%20to%20control%20multiple%20stages%20through%20vertical%20integration.%20For%20instance%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fpublications%2Fai-foundation-models-initial-report%5C%22%3EGoogle%20exemplifies%20a%20high%20level%20of%20integration%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20different%20stages%20of%20the%20supply%20chain.%20Its%20operations%20range%20from%20developing%20and%20training%20its%20own%20AI%20models%20on%20proprietary%20computing%20infrastructure%20using%20vast%20amounts%20of%20data%2C%20including%20proprietary%20data.%20It%20also%20offers%20cloud%20services%20and%20has%20integrated%20its%20AI%20systems%20into%20various%20applications%20for%20both%20web%20and%20Android%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20context%2C%20if%20India%20is%20to%20build%20a%20thriving%20domestic%20industry%20with%20local%20companies%20that%20can%20compete%20with%20global%20giants%2C%20AI%20governance%20will%20need%20to%20ensure%20unfettered%20access%20to%20the%20different%20stages%20of%20the%20supply%20chain.%20A%20number%20of%20primary%20considerations%20are%20necessary%20for%20each%20stage%20of%20the%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EData%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModels%20trained%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F2101.00027%5C%22%3Elarge%2C%20diverse%2C%20and%20high-quality%20data%20sets%20tend%20to%20perform%20better%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Studies%20estimate%20that%20for%20training%20large%20language%20models%2C%20high-quality%20data%20from%20sources%20such%20as%20books%2C%20academic%20papers%2C%20news%20articles%2C%20and%20Wikipedia%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F2211.04325%5C%22%3Elikely%20to%20be%20exhausted%20by%202027%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Thus%2C%20access%20to%20proprietary%20data%20can%20be%20a%20key%20differentiator%20for%20training%20AI%20models.%20This%20includes%20data%20such%20as%20the%20extensive%20code%20repositories%20available%20on%20GitHub%2C%20the%20sorted%20and%20categorised%20web%20index%20compiled%20by%20search%20engines%20from%20their%20web%20crawling%20activities%20or%20the%20audio%20and%20video%20recordings%20from%20video%20conferencing%20applications%20such%20as%20Zoom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBig%20tech%20platforms%20tend%20to%20be%20monopolies%20or%20duopolies%20due%20to%20the%20network%20effects.%20This%20market%20consolidation%20is%20evident%20across%20various%20platforms%2C%20ranging%20from%20search%20engines%20and%20social%20media%20to%20ride-sharing%20and%20food-delivery%20services.%20The%20scale%20and%20insight%20into%20user%20behavior%20from%20access%20to%20proprietary%20data%20help%20these%20companies%20innovate%20better%20than%20competitors.%20When%20developing%20AI%20applications%2C%20access%20to%20proprietary%20data%20gives%20these%20companies%20an%20edge.%20It%20also%20helps%20them%20integrate%20the%20AI%20applications%20into%20their%20existing%20offerings%2C%20thereby%20further%20consolidating%20market%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearch%20also%20shows%20that%20issues%20with%20fairness%20exist%20in%20AI%20use%20cases%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F31649194%2F%5C%22%3Emedical%20diagnoses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fproceedings.mlr.press%2Fv81%2Fbuolamwini18a%2Fbuolamwini18a.pdf%5C%22%3Egender%20classification%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.science.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1126%2Fsciadv.aao5580%5C%22%3Erecidivism%20prediction%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20other%20areas%20where%20certain%20groups%20are%20underrepresented%20in%20the%20training%20data.%20This%20can%20lead%20to%20higher%20error%20rates%20and%20biased%20outcomes%20for%20minorities%2C%20women%2C%20the%20elderly%2C%20and%20vulnerable%20populations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20India%E2%80%99s%20incredible%20diversity%2C%20the%20government%20could%20play%20an%20important%20role%20in%20creating%20publicly%20accessible%20open%20datasets%20that%20are%20representative%20of%20the%20population.%20Such%20datasets%20can%20have%20significant%20positive%20externalities%20for%20both%20research%20and%20commercial%20applications.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbhashini.gov.in%2Fabout-bhashini%5C%22%3EBhashini%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20such%20initiative%20under%20the%20Indian%20government%20that%20attempts%20to%20capture%20the%20diversity%20of%20Indian%20languages%20and%20provide%20open-source%20databases%20and%20tools%20for%20real-time%20translation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EComputation%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20training%20and%20usage%20typically%20relies%20on%20cloud%20computing%20services%20for%20computational%20infrastructure%2C%20a%20preferred%20choice%20for%20developers%20and%20users%20over%20owning%20the%20hardware.%20Cloud%20Service%20Providers%20(CSPs)%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fainowinstitute.org%2Fpublication%2Fpolicy%2Fcompute-and-ai%5C%22%3Eoffer%20substantial%20discounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20computing%20resources%20for%20AI%20research%20and%20development%2C%20aiming%20to%20secure%20a%20strong%20market%20position%20as%20the%20sector%20expands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20advantages%2C%20this%20model%20raises%20concerns.%20Due%20to%20the%20economies%20of%20scale%2C%20major%20CSPs%20such%20as%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%2C%20Microsoft%20Azure%2C%20and%20Google%20Cloud%20dominate%20the%20market%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcanalys.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fglobal-cloud-services-q3-2023%5C%22%3Ecollectively%20holding%20a%2065%25%20share%20globally%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20this%20market%20concentration%20is%20not%20a%20cause%20for%20concern%2C%20the%20leading%20CSPs%20also%20compete%20in%20other%20stages%20of%20the%20AI%20supply%20chain%2C%20including%20developing%20models%20and%20applications.%20Ensuring%20that%20vertical%20integration%20with%20cloud%20computing%20services%20does%20not%20hinder%20competition%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20supply%20chain%20is%20crucial.%20Competition%20regulators%20%E2%80%93%20including%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20must%20be%20vigilant%20about%20anti-competitive%20practices%20such%20as%20restrictive%20contracts%2C%20high%20costs%20for%20switching%20services%2C%20or%20unfair%20pricing%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20upstream%2C%20NVIDIA%2C%20a%20chip%20manufacturer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.networkworld.com%2Farticle%2F971778%2Fnvidia-still-crushing-the-data-center-market.html%5C%22%3Eholds%20more%20than%2090%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20market%20share%20for%20GPUs%2C%20the%20semiconductor%20chips%20essential%20for%20AI-related%20tasks.%20This%20market%20dominance%20stems%20from%20NVIDIA%E2%80%99s%20early%20entry%20into%20the%20market%20and%20the%20widespread%20adoption%20of%20its%20proprietary%20computing%20platform%2C%20CUDA.%20While%20intense%20competition%20is%20likely%20to%20create%20alternatives%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20this%20remains%20a%20geopolitical%20risk%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20mitigated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EModels%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bain.com%2Finsights%2Ffrom-buzz-to-reality-the-accelerating-pace-of-ai-in-india%2F%5C%22%3E%20report%20from%20Bain%20%26amp%3B%20Company%3C%2Fa%3E%20highlights%20that%20India%20is%20a%20leading%20AI%20talent%20hub%2C%20accounting%20for%2016%25%20of%20the%20global%20AI%20workforce%2C%20and%20positioning%20it%20among%20the%20top%20three%20in%20the%20world.%20However%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20notable%20scarcity%20of%20top-tier%20AI%20researchers%20in%20India%2C%20those%20engaged%20in%20generating%20intellectual%20property%20or%20in%20designing%20and%20training%20AI%20algorithms.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmacropolo.org%2Fdigital-projects%2Fthe-global-ai-talent-tracker%2F%5C%22%3EResearch%20by%20MacroPolo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20US%20think%20tank%2C%20indicates%20that%20over%2080%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20premier%20AI%20researchers%20relocate%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20trends%20suggest%20that%20due%20to%20the%20shortfall%20in%20specialised%20skills%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20barriers%20in%20the%20data%20and%20computation%20stages%2C%20Indian%20companies%20%E2%80%93%20which%20rely%20heavily%20on%20Indian%20talent%20%E2%80%93%20would%20find%20it%20challenging%20to%20create%20world%20class%20models.%20However%2C%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20compete%20effectively%20in%20other%20engineering%20skill-based%20tasks%20such%20as%20developing%20applications%20based%20on%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20developing%20cutting-edge%20AI%20models%20demands%20substantial%20data%2C%20computing%20power%2C%20and%20technical%20expertise%2C%20and%20the%20industry%20can%20mobilize%20these%20resources%20better%20than%20academia.%20This%20trend%20is%20underscored%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faiindex.stanford.edu%2Freport%2F%5C%22%3EStanford%20AI%20Index%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20reveals%20that%20in%202022%2C%20industry%20entities%20produced%20thirty-two%20significant%20machine%20learning%20models%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20academia%2C%20which%20contributed%20only%20three.%20Thus%2C%20government%20interventions%20to%20build%20AI%20capabilities%20should%20consider%20both%20the%20industry%20and%20academia%20as%20key%20contributors%20to%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EApplication%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20addressing%20concerns%20in%20other%20stages%20of%20the%20AI%20ecosystem%20will%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20a%20competitive%20market%20in%20the%20application%20stage.%20However%2C%20a%20framework%20to%20better%20manage%20risks%20associated%20with%20AI%20systems%20is%20required%20to%20ensure%20they%20are%20built%20responsibly.%20Alignment%20with%20AI%20risk%20management%20frameworks%2C%20such%20as%20the%20one%20developed%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fairc.nist.gov%2FAI_RMF_Knowledge_Base%2FPlaybook%5C%22%3EUS%E2%80%99s%20National%20Institute%20of%20Standards%20and%20Technology%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20can%20help%20systematically%20assess%20and%20mitigate%20risks%20across%20the%20development%20life%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20global%20efforts%20are%20underway%20to%20better%20understand%20and%20govern%20AI%2C%20the%20Indian%20state%20needs%20to%20consider%20its%20unique%20conditions%20and%20the%20current%20geopolitical%20climate%20to%20take%20measures%20to%20ensure%20access%20to%20the%20technology%20and%20the%20benefits%20it%20has%20to%20offer.%20This%20article%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftakshashila.org.in%2Fresearch%2Fa-pathway-to-ai-governance%5C%22%3Ediscussion%20document%20on%20which%20it%20is%20based%3C%2Fa%3E%20focus%20on%20AI%20governance%20from%20a%20national%20interest%20perspective%2C%20highlighting%20some%20of%20the%20primary%20concerns%20at%20each%20stage%20of%20the%20AI%20supply%20chain.%20Recognizing%20these%20concerns%20is%20crucial%2C%20as%20they%20lay%20the%20groundwork%20for%20shaping%20targeted%20policy%20measures%20tailored%20to%20each%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EBharath%20Reddy%20is%20a%20researcher%20in%20the%20High-Tech%20Geopolitics%20programme%20at%20the%20Takshashila%20Institution.%20He%20is%20a%20co-author%20with%20Nitin%20Pai%2C%20Satya%20Shoova%20Sahu%2C%20Rijesh%20Panicker%20and%20Sridhar%20Krishna%20on%20Takshashila%E2%80%99s%20discussion%20document%20on%20AI%20Governance.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20in%20Transition%3C%2Fem%3E%20(%3Cem%3EIiT%3C%2Fem%3E)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcasi.sas.upenn.edu%2Fiit%2Fbharathreddy%5C%22%3Eis%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Center%20for%20the%20Advanced%20Study%20of%20India%20(CASI)%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania.%20All%20viewpoints%2C%20positions%2C%20and%20conclusions%20expressed%20in%20%3Cem%3EIiT%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20solely%20those%20of%20the%20author(s)%20and%20not%20specifically%20those%20of%20CASI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcasi.sas.upenn.edu%2Fiit%2Fbharathreddy%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20CASI%20website.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709114794000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08091601%2Fartificial-intelligence-2167835_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fbuilding-the-yard-policy-considerations-for-ai-in-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AI%20is%20projected%20to%20greatly%20improve%20governance%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20education%20outcomes.%20However%2C%20this%20potential%20may%20not%20be%20realised%20if%20the%20building%20blocks%20of%20AI%20remain%20concentrated%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20few%20dominant%20firms%20or%20the%20countries%20in%20which%20they%20are%20located.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fbuilding-the-yard-policy-considerations-for-ai-in-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bill%20Gates%20visits%20Microsoft's%20India%20Development%20Center%20in%20Hyderabad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709114781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-06%2F06%2Ffull%2F1686046036-9475.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbill-gates-visits-microsoft-s-india-development-center-in-hyderabad-124022800563_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Billionaire%20philanthropist%20and%20Microsoft%20co-founder%20Bill%20Gates%20visited%20the%20tech%20giant's%20India%20Development%20Center%20(IDC)%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20the%20company%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbill-gates-visits-microsoft-s-india-development-center-in-hyderabad-124022800563_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.