%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2055th%20session%20of%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20kicked%20off%20on%20Monday%2C%20February%2026%2C%20and%20will%20continue%20until%20April%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReproduced%20below%20is%20the%20full%20statement%20of%20Volker%20T%C3%BCrk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20of%20the%20General%20Assembly%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnSecretary-General%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnPresident%20of%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Council%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnExcellencies%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnDistinguished%20delegates%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Council%20enters%20into%20session%20at%20a%20time%20of%20seismic%20global%20shocks.%20Conflicts%20are%20battering%20the%20lives%20of%20millions%20of%20civilians%2C%20and%20carving%20even%20deeper%20fault-lines%20across%20and%20between%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pain%20and%20the%20slaughter%20of%20so%20many%20people%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20Sudan%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20Haiti%20and%20so%20many%20other%20places%20around%20the%20world%20are%20unbearable.%20And%20when%20we%20discuss%2C%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%2C%20country%20after%20country%2C%20we%20must%20remember%20their%20faces%20and%20their%20anguish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20of%20such%20atrocious%20violations%2C%20is%20it%20na%C3%AFve%20to%20demand%20that%20all%20States%20uphold%20their%20human%20rights%20commitments%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOr%20is%20it%20crucial%20%E2%80%93%20the%20most%20important%2C%20the%20most%20consequential%2C%20the%20most%20urgent%20task%20that%20any%20of%20us%20could%20possibly%20undertake%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20these%20not%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20our%20only%20guarantees%2C%20essential%2C%20and%20profoundly%20rooted%2C%20anchoring%20our%20societies%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20turbulence%20and%20disarray%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMember%20States%20and%20many%20partners%20came%20together%20at%20the%20December%20high-level%20event%20to%20commemorate%2075%20years%20of%20the%20Universal%20Declaration%20of%20Human%20Rights.%20This%20was%20an%20important%20moment%20of%20reflection%20on%20the%20successes%20and%20failures%20to%20implement%20human%20rights%2C%20and%20how%20we%20can%20do%20better%20in%20the%20future.%20It%20was%20the%20culmination%20of%20a%20rich%2C%20year-long%20engagement%20across%20the%20world%20which%20resounded%20with%20demands%20that%20the%20world%20deliver%20on%20the%20promises%20of%20the%20Universal%20Declaration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemands%20for%20action%20to%20end%20conflicts.%20To%20eradicate%20discrimination.%20To%20heal%20our%20distorted%20economies%20and%20our%20battered%20environment.%20Demands%20for%20quality%20services%2C%20such%20as%20education%20and%20healthcare.%20For%20an%20end%20to%20corruption.%20For%20a%20voice%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20future.%20And%20over%20and%20over%20again%2C%20demands%20that%20States%20change%20course%20%E2%80%93%20to%20bring%20humanity%20the%20benefits%20of%20greater%20justice%2C%20more%20inclusive%20development%2C%20greater%20equality%2C%20and%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20that%20two-day%20event%2C%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3E153%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0Member%20States%20had%20issued%20concrete%20pledges%2C%20alongside%20civil%20society%20groups%2C%20UN%20bodies%2C%20businesses%20and%20others%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fhuman-rights-75%2Fpledge%2Fhuman-rights-75-pledges%5C%22%3Eover%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3E770%20pledges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20all.%20They%20ranged%20from%20commitments%20to%20increase%20women%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20and%20employment%20equality%2C%20to%20tackling%20extreme%20poverty%2C%20ensuring%20transitional%20justice%2C%20and%20improving%20access%20to%20education%2C%20healthcare%20and%20social%20protections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20important%20was%20the%20outpouring%20of%20support%20from%20members%20of%20the%20public%2C%20in%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20globe.%20The%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.opensocietyfoundations.org%2Fuploads%2Fbe67f098-4fdf-45ce-adeb-5143e8282d23%2Fbarometer-in-context-strengthening-the-human-rights-system-20231208.pdf%5C%22%3EOpen%20Society%20Barometer%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%93%20a%20survey%20of%20over%2036%2C000%20people%20in%2030%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20found%20that%20the%20vast%20majority%20agreed%20that%20human%20rights%20have%20been%20a%20%E2%80%9Cforce%20for%20good.%E2%80%9D%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20silent%20majority%20holds%20to%20the%20human%20rights%20principles%20that%20ensure%20progress%20and%20justice%20across%20all%20societies%2C%20and%20which%20keep%20our%20world%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20I%20am%20pleased%20to%20launch%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2Fen%2Fdocuments%2Foutcome-documents%2Fhuman-rights-path-solutions%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHuman%20Rights%3A%20A%20Path%20for%20Solutions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C%2C%20the%20distillation%20of%20the%20work%20that%20has%20gone%20into%20our%20commemoration%20year%2C%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20it%20will%20inform%20the%20Summit%20of%20the%20Future.%20It%20sets%20out%20eight%20messages%20to%20guide%20renewed%20action%20for%20peace%3B%20economies%20that%20work%20for%20people%20and%20planet%3B%20effective%20governance%3B%20and%20guardrails%20for%20digital%20and%20scientific%20progress.%20Itbroadens%20the%20way%20we%20think%20about%20rights%2C%20in%20ways%20that%20can%20transform%20societies%20and%20our%20global%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Secretary-General%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20of%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EProtection%20Pledge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20and%20the%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EAgenda%20for%20Protection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20entire%20UN%20gives%20priority%20to%20advancing%20human%20rights%20in%20every%20circumstance%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20challenging.%20I%20look%20forward%20to%20working%20with%20colleagues%20across%20the%20UN%20to%20implement%20this%20Pledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20will%20address%20various%20country%20situations%20throughout%20this%20Council%20session%2C%20and%20in%20particular%2C%20in%20the%20global%20update%20next%20Monday.%20But%20this%20morning%20I%20would%20like%20to%20flag%20two%20overarching%20concerns%20that%20have%20potential%20impact%20on%20all%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20negotiations%20on%20treaties%20on%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Epandemic%20prevention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0and%20on%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Ecybercrime%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20on%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Eplastic%20pollution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3B%20and%20global%20discussions%20about%20the%20regulation%20of%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20all%20these%20talks%20tare%20currently%20underway%2C%20but%20they%20are%20not%20sufficiently%20taking%20into%20account%20human%20rights%20obligations%2C%20and%20the%20human%20rights%20harms%20that%20could%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20I%20am%20disturbed%20by%20attempts%20to%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Eundermine%20the%20legitimacy%20and%20work%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20other%20institutions.%20They%20include%20disinformation%20that%20targets%20UN%20humanitarian%20organizations%2C%20UN%20peacekeepers%20and%20my%20Office.%20The%20UN%20has%20become%20a%20lightning%20rod%20for%20manipulative%20propaganda%20and%20a%20scapegoat%20for%20policy%20failures.%20This%20is%20profoundly%20destructive%20of%20the%20common%20good%2C%20and%20it%20callously%20betrays%20the%20many%20people%20whose%20lives%20rely%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20is%20uniquely%20equipped%20to%20enable%20States%20to%20discuss%20and%20resolve%20pressing%20global%20issues%20%E2%80%93%20and%20this%20convening%20power%20is%20particularly%20vital%20now%2C%20when%20the%20magnitude%20of%20conflict%2C%20planetary%20peril%20and%20digital%20transformation%20requires%20urgent%20solutions.%20UN%20humanitarian%20agencies%20assist%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20people%20to%20stay%20alive.%20The%20UN%E2%80%99s%20development%20and%20peace%20work%20is%20absolutely%20crucial%20to%20all%20nations.%20My%20Office%20is%20mandated%20to%20monitor%20and%20report%20on%20human%20rights%20because%20States%20have%20agreed%20that%20rights%20and%20justice%20are%20the%20best%2C%20and%20only%2C%20way%20forward.%20The%20work%20of%20opening%20dialogues%20and%20protecting%20rights%20is%20not%20comfortable%20for%20everyone%20%E2%80%93%20but%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20all%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20overcome%20the%20binary%20view%20that%20if%20you%20are%20not%20for%20us%2C%20and%20against%20our%20enemies%2C%20then%20you%20too%20must%20be%20an%20enemy.%20Within%20countries%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cus%20versus%20them%E2%80%9D%20illogic%20is%20creating%20increasingly%20dangerous%20and%20combustible%20divisions%2C%20especially%20in%20pre-electoral%20periods%2C%20of%20which%20there%20are%20many%20this%20year.%20All%20this%20is%20a%20politics%20of%20distraction%2C%20of%20warmongering%2C%20which%20slowly%20numbs%20our%20deepest%20sense%20of%20compassion.%20Especially%20at%20a%20time%20of%20deep%20division%20and%20fear%2C%20seeing%20the%20humanity%20in%20the%20other%20is%20the%20lifeline%20that%20can%20tug%20us%20away%20from%20disaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20draw%20strength%20and%20hope%20from%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20powerful%20tributes%20to%20the%20Universal%20Declaration%20of%20Human%20Rights%20%E2%80%93%20the%20testimonies%20we%20heard%20from%20so%20many%20people%2C%20and%20the%20significant%20pledges%20that%20were%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20power%20of%20human%20rights%20is%20rooted%20in%20their%20universality%20%E2%80%93%20the%20equal%20value%20of%20every%20human%20life%20that%20is%20at%20their%20core.%20The%20same%20human%20rights%20standards%20must%20be%20deployed%20everywhere%2C%20and%20they%20must%20be%20benchmarks%20for%20future%20progress%20%E2%80%93%20not%20high-water%20marks%20from%20which%20we%20can%20recede.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20human%20being%20is%20born%20equal.%20All%20victims%20are%20equally%20deserving%20of%20justice.%20No-one%20can%20be%20left%20behind.%20And%20nobody%20is%20above%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThank%20you%2C%20Mr%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709112561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28140350%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fun-human-rights-councils-55th-summit-kicks-off-with-renewed-action-for-peace%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22United%20Nations%C2%A0High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights%2C%C2%A0Volker%20T%C3%BCrk%2C%20released%20a%20new%20vision%20statement%20offering%20solutions%20to%20pressing%20human%20rights%20concerns%20globally.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fun-human-rights-councils-55th-summit-kicks-off-with-renewed-action-for-peace%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Air%20India%20Express%20looking%20to%20operate%2040%25%20more%20flights%20next%20fiscal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709112218000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-03%2F27%2Ffull%2F1679927845-8786.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fair-india-express-looking-to-operate-40-more-flights-next-fiscal-124022800535_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Air%20India%20Express%20currently%20operates%20350%20daily%20flights%20and%20has%20a%20fleet%20of%2069%20planes%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fair-india-express-looking-to-operate-40-more-flights-next-fiscal-124022800535_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fair-india-expr