com%2Findia%2Fchina-says-envoy-to-visit-ukraine-russia-eu-states-this-week%2Farticleshow%2F108067652.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fchina-says-envoy-to-visit-ukraine-russia-eu-states-this-week%2Famp_articleshow%2F108067652.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fchina-says-envoy-to-visit-ukraine-russia-eu-states-this-week%2Famp_articleshow%2F108067652.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elephant%20spins%20tourist%20around%20before%20slamming%20her%20to%20ground%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709107440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F70x70%2Fskynews-india-jaipur-elephant_6471869.jpg%3F20240228104054%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftourists-leg-broken-after-elephant-attack-13082708%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20tourist%20had%20her%20leg%20broken%20after%20being%20grabbed%20by%20an%20elephant%20and%20slammed%20to%20the%20ground.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftourists-leg-broken-after-elephant-attack-13082708%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ftourists-leg-broken-after-elephant-attack-13082708%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ftourists-leg-broken-after-elephant-attack-13082708%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Danger%20of%20Reading%20Too%20Much%20Into%20IQ%20Tests%20and%20the%20Crucial%20Cognitive%20Skills%20They%20Don%E2%80%99t%26nbsp%3BMeasure%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28131036%2F1636530118phpWsuZ5B.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20object%20to%20intelligence%20tests.%20Some%20say%20IQ%20test%20scores%20are%20too%20often%20abused.%20They%20says%20it%E2%80%99s%20unfair%20that%20when%20children%20%E2%80%9Cfail%E2%80%9D%20these%20tests%20it%20can%20mean%20they%20receive%20a%20worse%20secondary%20education%20than%20their%20more%20successful%20peers%20%E2%80%93%20sentencing%20them%20to%20a%20lifetime%20of%20disadvantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20object%20to%20IQ%20tests%20for%20quite%20personal%20reasons%20and%20remember%20how%20stressed%20they%20were%20by%20sitting%20a%20test.%20Many%20doubt%20their%20result%20was%20a%20fair%20reflection%20of%20their%20future%20potential.%20But%20how%20useful%20are%20IQ%20tests%20really%20%E2%80%93%20and%20what%20skills%20and%20qualities%20do%20they%20miss%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20discovered%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhomepages.abdn.ac.uk%2Fj.crawford%2Fpages%2Fdept%2Fpdfs%2FIntelligence_2000_Stability_IQ.pdf%5C%22%3Ehalf-forgotten%2C%20unique%20archive%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20more%20than%2089%2C000%20IQ-type%20tests%20from%201932.%20This%20comprised%20a%20near-complete%20national%20sample%20of%20Scottish%20children%20born%20in%201921%20who%20%E2%80%93%20at%20the%20time%20%E2%80%93%20would%20have%20been%20about%2076%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20aim%20was%20simple%3A%20to%20find%20local%20people%20to%20match%20with%20the%20archive%20and%20compare%20their%20current%20mental%20ability%20with%20their%20test%20result%20from%201932.%20A%20picture%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1136%2Fbmj.322.7290.819%5C%22%3Equickly%20emerged%3C%2Fa%3E%20linking%20lower%20IQ%20scores%20with%20earlier%20than%20expected%20age%20at%20death%20and%20earlier%20onset%20dementia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20world%20war%20yielded%20some%20strong%20unexpected%20anomalies.%20Young%20men%20with%20higher%20childhood%20IQ%20scores%20more%20often%20died%20on%20active%20service.%20Girls%20with%20higher%20scores%20more%20often%20moved%20away%20from%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20cycled%20around%20Aberdeen%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20its%20social%20history%2C%20becoming%20familiar%20with%20the%20primary%20schools%20where%20the%20children%20had%20sat%20their%20tests%20in%201932.%20Average%20IQ%20scores%20often%20differed%20substantially%20between%20schools.%20Those%20pupils%20attending%20schools%20in%20overcrowded%20districts%20tended%20to%20perform%20less%20well%20on%20the%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20later%20research%20showed%20that%20people%20with%20higher%20IQ%20were%20engaging%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bmj.com%2Fcontent%2F363%2Fbmj.k4925%5C%22%3Emore%20intellectually%20stimulating%20activities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20reading%20complex%20novels%20or%20learning%20musical%20instruments.%20But%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20know%20whether%20having%20a%20high%20IQ%20leads%20people%20to%20seek%20out%20such%20activities%20or%20whether%20intellectually%20curious%20people%20develop%20higher%20IQ%20because%20they%20engage%20in%20cognitively%20complex%20tasks%20throughout%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%E2%80%99s%20an%20important%20question.%20People%20from%20poorer%20backgrounds%2C%20such%20as%20the%20disadvantaged%20neighbourhoods%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Aberdeen%2C%20may%20not%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20pursue%20intellectual%20interests%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20time%20and%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20better%20inform%20my%20work%2C%20I%20sought%20out%20local%20residents%20with%20long%20experience%20of%20teaching%20in%20Aberdeen.%20Their%20views%20were%20echoed%20by%20current%20workers%20in%20public%20health%20and%20psychology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeachers%20warned%20me%20not%20to%20forget%20that%20IQ%20tests%20have%20been%20used%20over%20the%20years%20to%20advance%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvia.library.depaul.edu%2Fcgi%2Fviewcontent.cgi%3Farticle%3D1270%26context%3Dlaw-review%5C%22%3Escientific%20racism%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20they%20feared%20that%20before%20too%20long%2C%20right-wing%20advocates%20of%20IQ%20testing%20would%20want%20to%20use%20these%20rediscovered%20Scottish%20data%20to%20search%20for%20the%20genetic%20basis%20of%20intelligence.%20Alarmed%20and%20now%20forewarned%2C%20I%20looked%20back%20at%20the%20reasons%20for%20undertaking%20the%201932%20survey%20of%20the%20mental%20ability%20of%20Scottish%20schoolchildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20was%20funded%20by%20the%20Eugenics%20Society%20(eugenics%20is%20the%20science%20of%20improving%20the%20human%20race%20through%20the%20selection%20of%20%E2%80%9Cgood%E2%80%9D%20hereditary%20traits)%20with%20some%20help%20from%20the%20Rockefeller%20Foundation.%20Their%20shared%20priority%20was%20to%20show%20a%20link%20between%20large%20family%20size%20and%20below%20average%20mental%20ability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20this%20negative%20relationship%20between%20a%20mothers%E2%80%99%20IQ%20and%20having%20children%20was%20easy%20to%20show.%20But%20post-1945%20educational%20reforms%2C%20which%20led%20to%20more%20girls%20completing%20higher%20education%2C%20produced%20much%20more%20complex%20relationships%20between%20maternal%20IQ%2C%20educational%20achievements%2C%20age%20at%20first%20childbirth%20and%20lifetime%20fertility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20fed%20into%20contemporary%20public%20concerns%20that%20the%20average%20mental%20ability%20of%20the%20general%20population%20was%20lowered%20by%20the%20loss%20of%20so%20many%20young%20men%20of%20presumed%20above%20average%20ability%20during%20the%20first%20world%20war%20war.%20Newspapers%20argued%20that%20schoolboys%20would%20need%20to%20be%20assessed%20and%20selected%20to%20better%20educate%20those%20most%20likely%20to%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20only%20goes%20to%20show%20that%20while%20IQ%20tests%20can%20tell%20us%20something%20about%20academic%20success%20or%20dementia%20risk%2C%20they%20miss%20a%20lot%20of%20a%20nuance.%20There%E2%80%99s%20no%20denying%20they%20have%20long%20been%20used%20for%20murky%20reasons%20%E2%80%93%20often%20as%20an%20excuse%20to%20direct%20less%20funding%20to%20certain%20types%20of%20school%2C%20thereby%20creating%20a%20two-tier%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20children%2C%20those%20who%20do%20not%20take%20or%20pass%20IQ-style%20entrance%20exams%20to%20private%20or%20grammar%20schools%2C%20will%20have%20many%20qualities%20not%20measured%20on%20an%20IQ%20test.%20They%20may%20also%20just%20be%20late%20developers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20IQ%20tests%20don%E2%80%99t%20measure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20do%20IQ%20tests%20miss%3F%20Research%20suggests%20that%20IQ%20scores%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fiq-tests-are-humans-getting-smarter-158837%5C%22%3Erose%20by%20about%203%20points%20per%20decade%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20much%20of%20the%2020th%20century%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpsycnet.apa.org%2Frecord%2F2012-26835-000%5C%22%3Emay%20have%20dropped%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20past%2030%20years%20or%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%20argue%20this%20reflects%20changes%20in%20the%20school%20curriculum%20or%20maybe%20just%20the%20complexity%20of%20modern%20life.%20The%20acquisition%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccontent%20knowledge%E2%80%9D%20(reading%20and%20memorising)%20once%20formed%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20public%20examinations%20and%20is%20related%20to%20IQ%20test%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20for%20example%20that%20working%20memory%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS1041608002000493%5C%22%3Eis%20related%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20IQ%20test%20performance.%20But%20research%20has%20since%20uncovered%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1111%2Fj.1467-9280.2005.01641.x%5C%22%3Eself-discipline%20is%20actually%20better%20predictor%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20exam%20results%20than%20IQ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENowadays%2C%20children%20in%20the%20west%20are%20taught%20collective%20scientific%20problem-solving%2C%20combined%20with%20interpersonal%20skills%20and%20teamwork%2C%20which%20requires%20less%20memorisation%20(rote%20learning).%20This%20may%20actually%20make%20students%20less%20likely%20to%20score%20highly%20on%20IQ%20tests%2C%20even%20though%20these%20methods%20are%20helping%20humanity%20as%20a%20whole%20get%20smarter.%20Knowledge%20keeps%20growing%2C%20often%20as%20a%20result%20of%20giant%20research%20collaborations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20type%20of%20%E2%80%9Cprocedural%20learning%E2%80%9D%20leads%20to%20mature%20self-awareness%2C%20emotional%20stability%2C%20recognition%20of%20the%20thoughts%20and%20feelings%20of%20others%20and%20an%20understanding%20of%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20impact%20on%20the%20performance%20of%20a%20group.%20Critically%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20these%20skills%20can%20hinder%20rational%20thinking.%20Research%20shows%20that%20when%20we%20ignore%20or%20fail%20to%20understand%20our%20feelings%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Foro.open.ac.uk%2F31984%2F%23%3A%257E%3Atext%3DWe%2520conclude%2520that%2520emotions%2520and%2Cfor%2520trader%2520behavior%2520and%2520performance.%5C%22%3Ewe%20are%20more%20easily%20manipulated%20by%20them%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHigh%20IQ%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20protect%20against%20bias%20or%20error%20either.%20In%20fact%2C%20research%20shows%20that%20people%20with%20high%20IQ%20can%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Freview-the-intelligence-trap-why-smart-people-do-stupid-things-and-how-to-make-wiser-decisions-by-david-robson-impressive-and-readable-tgr72mshs%2F%5C%22%3Eparticularly%20vulnerable%20to%20mistakes%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20spotting%20patterns%20even%20when%20there%20aren%E2%80%99t%20any%2C%20or%20they%20are%20irrelevant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20may%20lead%20to%20confirmation%20bias%20and%20difficulty%20giving%20up%20on%20an%20idea%2C%20solution%20or%20project%20even%20when%20it%20is%20no%20longer%20working.%20This%20can%20also%20get%20in%20the%20way%20of%20rational%20reasoning.%20But%20such%20weaknesses%20are%20missed%20by%20IQ%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(min-width%3A%201466px)%20754px%2C%20(max-width%3A%20599px)%20100vw%2C%20(min-width%3A%20600px)%20600px%2C%20237px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F577001%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20240221-30-nfj86z.jpg%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26q%3D45%26auto%3Dformat%26w%3D237%26fit%3Dclip%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Image%20of%20Albert%20Einstein.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22353%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F577001%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20240221-30-nfj86z.jpg%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26amp%3Bq%3D45%26amp%3Bauto%3Dformat%26amp%3Bw%3D600%26amp%3Bh%3D800%26amp%3Bfit%3Dcrop%26amp%3Bdpr%3D1%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F577001%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20240221-30-nfj86z.jpg%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26amp%3Bq%3D30%26amp%3Bauto%3Dformat%26amp%3Bw%3D600%26amp%3Bh%3D800%26amp%3Bfit%3Dcrop%26amp%3Bdpr%3D2%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F577001%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20240221-30-nfj86z.jpg%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26amp%3Bq%3D15%26amp%3Bauto%3Dformat%26amp%3Bw%3D600%26amp%3Bh%3D800%26amp%3Bfit%3Dcrop%26amp%3Bdpr%3D3%201800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F577001%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20240221-30-nfj86z.jpg%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26amp%3Bq%3D45%26amp%3Bauto%3Dformat%26amp%3Bw%3D754%26amp%3Bh%3D1005%26amp%3Bfit%3Dcrop%26amp%3Bdpr%3D1%20754w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F577001%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20240221-30-nfj86z.jpg%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26amp%3Bq%3D30%26amp%3Bauto%3Dformat%26amp%3Bw%3D754%26amp%3Bh%3D1005%26amp%3Bfit%3Dcrop%26amp%3Bdpr%3D2%201508w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fimages.theconversation.com%2Ffiles%2F577001%2Foriginal%2Ffile-20240221-30-nfj86z.jpg%3Fixlib%3Drb-1.1.0%26amp%3Bq%3D15%26amp%3Bauto%3Dformat%26amp%3Bw%3D754%26amp%3Bh%3D1005%26amp%3Bfit%3Dcrop%26amp%3Bdpr%3D3%202262w%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22471%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cspan%3EEinstein%20valued%20creativity%20and%20intuition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewikipedia%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fcreativecommons.org%2Flicenses%2Fby-sa%2F4.0%2F%5C%22%3ECC%20BY-SA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20great%20leaps%20in%20human%20ingenuity%20were%20driven%20by%20creativity%2C%20collaboration%2C%20competition%2C%20intuition%20or%20curiosity%20rather%20than%20just%20individual%20IQ.%20Take%20Albert%20Einstein%2C%20who%20is%20often%20hailed%20as%20a%20genius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20never%20took%20an%20IQ%20test%2C%20but%20people%20are%20constantly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Fparenting%2Fmoments%2F5-genius-kids-who-have-an-iq-score-higher-than-albert-einstein%2Fphotostory%2F99929937.cms%5C%22%3Especulating%20about%20his%20IQ%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Yet%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weforum.org%2Fagenda%2F2019%2F08%2Falbert-einstein-quotes-inspiring-clever-funny-famous%2F%23%3A%257E%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CThe%2520important%2520thing%2520is%2520not%2Cof%2520this%2520mystery%2520every%2520day.%25E2%2580%259D%5C%22%3Eoften%20credited%20curiosity%20and%20intuition%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20core%20driving%20forces%20of%20scientific%20success%20%E2%80%93%20and%20these%20are%20not%20qualities%20measured%20by%20an%20IQ%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ethos%20of%20a%20modern%20school%20is%20rightly%20not%20driven%20by%20a%20preference%20to%20educate%20only%20those%20children%20who%20on%20selection%20meet%20a%20minimum%20standard%20on%20a%20mental%20test.%20Schools%20acknowledge%20that%20educational%20outcomes%20are%20not%20determined%20solely%20by%20any%20innate%20ability%20but%20are%20equally%20affected%20by%20all%20prior%20experiences%20that%20affect%20emotional%20competences%2C%20motivation%2C%20intellectual%20curiosity%2C%20insightfulness%20and%20intuitive%20reasoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20local%20participants%20in%20the%201932%20survey%20were%20interviewed%20in%20late%20life%2C%20they%20spoke%20warmly%20of%20their%20schooldays%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20about%20friendships.%20They%20rarely%20mentioned%20their%20education%20though.%20The%20learning%20of%20content%20knowledge%2C%20with%20threats%20of%20physical%20punishments%2C%20simply%20weren%E2%80%99t%20well%20regarded.%20Some%20remembered%20sitting%20the%20IQ%20test%20in%201932%20and%20were%20pleased%20most%20schools%20no%20longer%20test%20children%20that%20way.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F223570%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Flawrence-whalley-615876%5C%22%3ELawrence%20Whalley%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Emeritus%20Professor%20of%20Mental%20Health%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Finstitutions%2Funiversity-of-aberdeen-962%5C%22%3EUniversity%20of%20Aberdeen%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fiq-tests-the-danger-of-reading-too-much-into-them-and-the-crucial-cognitive-skills-they-dont-measure-223570%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709107334000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28131036%2F1636530118phpWsuZ5B.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fscience%2Fthe-danger-of-reading-too-much-into-iq-tests-and-the-crucial-cognitive-skills-they-dont-measure%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20great%20leaps%20in%20human%20ingenuity%20were%20driven%20by%20creativity%2C%20collaboration%2C%20intuition%20or%20curiosity%20rather%20than%20just%20individual%20IQ.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fscience%2Fthe-danger-of-reading-too-much-into-iq-tests-and-the-crucial-cognitive-skills-they-dont-measure%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reliance%20Capital%20to%20be%20delisted%20from%20stock%20exchanges%2C%20shares%20drop%204.46%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709107316000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2019-05%2F23%2Ffull%2F1558626884-8887.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-capital-to-be-delisted-from-stock-exchanges-shares-drop-4-46-124022800451_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22RCL%20said%20that%20the%20National%20Company%20Law%20Tribunal%20in%20its%20approved%20resolution%20plan%20for%20the%20company%20is%20contemplating%20delisting%20of%20existing%20equity%20shares%20from%20the%20exchanges%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-capital-to-be-delisted-from-stock-exchanges-shares-drop-4-46-124022800451_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-capital-to-be-delisted-from-stock-exchanges-shares-drop-4-46-124022800451_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-capital-to-be-delisted-from-stock-exchanges-shares-drop-4-46-124022800451_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JP%20Morgan%20Executive%20Alleges%20Caste%20Discrimination%20in%20Gujarat%20Housing%20Complex%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28124724%2FScreenshot-2024-02-28-at-12.47.13-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20robust%20business%20district%20with%20vast%20acres%20of%20commercial%20and%20residential%20spaces%2C%20the%20Gift%20City%20is%20rapidly%20consolidating%20its%20position%20as%20a%20powerhouse%20of%20financial%20and%20IT%20services.%20Its%20cutting-edge%20infrastructure%20continues%20to%20attract%20numerous%20startups.%20What%20furthers%20the%20Gift%20City%E2%80%99s%20allure%20is%20the%20job%20boom%20it%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20vision%20made%20a%20vice-president%20of%20JP%20Morgan%2C%20Anirudh%20Kejriwal%2C%20choose%20Gujarat%20over%20Singapore%20when%20he%20got%20an%20opportunity.%20Originally%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20Anirudh%20has%20graduated%20from%20IIT%20Guwahati.%20He%20was%20born%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20this%20pan-national%20exposure%20makes%20him%20a%20true%20Indian%20exposed%20to%20different%20cultures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnirudh%20decided%20to%20buy%20a%20house%20near%20Koba%20in%20Gandhinagar%20which%20is%20close%20to%20GIFT%20city%20from%20where%20he%20has%20been%20functioning%20for%20about%20three%20months.%20%E2%80%9C%20I%20zeroed%20in%20on%20a%20house%20that%20I%20like%20at%20Sant%20Vihar%20I%20society.%20The%20house%20was%20going%20to%20cost%20me%20Rs%2070%20lacs.%20I%20gave%20Rs%2035%20lacs%20via%20a%20cheque%20to%20the%20house%20owner%2C%20Baldevbhai%20Patel%20from%20whom%20I%20was%20going%20to%20buy%20the%20house%20in%20a%20resale%20deed%E2%80%9D%2C%20Anirudh%20told%20%3Cem%3EVibes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20house%20owner%20kept%20on%20delaying%20giving%20him%20the%20No%20Objection%20Certificate%20(NOC).%20According%20to%20Anirudh%2C%20the%20society%20which%20has%20a%20majority%20of%20Patels%20did%20not%20want%20a%20non%20Gujarati%20with%20the%20surname%20Kejriwal%20buying%20a%20house.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20Hindu%3B%20I%20am%20a%20vegetarian%2C%20I%20told%20him%E2%80%9D%2C%20Anirudh%20added%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20was%20discriminated%20against%20by%20the%20housing%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnirudh%20took%20to%20X%20to%20express%20his%20anguish.%20He%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20living%20in%20Mumbai%20for%20years%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Gujarat%2C%20choosing%20it%20over%20an%20opportunity%20in%20Singapore.%20I%20was%20captivated%20by%20the%20promise%20of%20GIFT%20City%20and%20the%20grand%20vision%20our%20prime%20minister%20and%20government%20laid%20out%20for%20us.%20It%20inspired%20me%20so%20much%20that%20I%20took%20a%20big%20step%20and%20decided%20to%20buy%20my%20first%20house%20here%2C%20dreaming%20of%20a%20future%20filled%20with%20hope%20and%20growth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20facing%20unexpected%20challenges%20with%20my%20dream%20home%2C%20barred%20from%20moving%20in%2C%20not%20because%20of%20anything%20I%20have%20done%2C%20but%20because%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20born%20Gujarati.%20Worse%20yet%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20warned%20that%20even%20if%20I%20manage%20to%20get%20in%2C%20happiness%20will%20be%20out%20of%20reach%2C%20and%20troubles%20will%20follow.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20bitter%20pill%20to%20swallow.%20Choosing%20Gujarat%2C%20leaving%20behind%20my%20life%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20the%20chance%20to%20move%20to%20Singapore%2C%20I%20never%20thought%20I%E2%80%99d%20face%20such%20discrimination.%20This%20experience%20has%20been%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20nightmare.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Anirudh%2C%20it%20is%20because%20of%20his%20caste%20and%20community%20that%20he%20is%20being%20discriminated%20against.%20Anirudh%20said%20he%20is%20seeking%20legal%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Flets-talk-about-housing-discrimination%5C%22%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20Talk%20About%20Housing%20Discrimination%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%3Cem%3EVibes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20visited%20Sant%20Vihar%20Society%20and%20though%20the%20majority%20of%20residents%20are%20indeed%20Patels%2C%20there%20are%20few%20others%20also%20who%20have%20purchased%20houses.%20There%20are%2092%20flats%20in%20the%20complex.%20The%20society%20chairman%2C%20Laljibhai%20Patel%20claimed%20that%20this%20was%20not%20an%20issue%20of%20caste%20or%20community%20discrimination%20but%20some%20personal%20problem%20between%20the%20house%20owner%20and%20the%20buyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnirudh%20maintains%20that%20he%20has%20been%20barred%20from%20buying%20the%20flat%20because%20of%20%E2%80%9Cbeing%20a%20Kejriwal%E2%80%9D.%20His%20fault%3F%20He%20was%20a%20Mumbai-kar%2C%20not%20a%20born%20Gujarati.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20situation%20escalated%20quickly%20with%20nearly%2030%20people%20gathering%2C%20threatening%20me%20with%20dire%20consequences%20if%20I%20proceeded%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kejriwal%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Kejriwal%20is%20determined%20to%20reclaim%20his%20rights%20and%20even%20pursue%20legal%20options%20if%20necessary.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20my%20preparations%2C%20from%20financial%20investments%20to%20personal%20arrangements%2C%20are%20now%20in%20jeopardy%20due%20to%20this%20discrimination.%20The%20vision%20of%20an%20inclusive%20India%20feels%20tarnished%20in%20the%20very%20state%20leading%20India%E2%80%99s%20development%20narrative%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESympathies%20poured%20in%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20one%20user%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20not%20surprised%2C%20despite%20all%20the%20claims%20of%20modernity%20the%20thinking%20of%20many%20people%20here%20is%20extremely%20backward.%20Caste-based%20discrimination%20is%20rampant%20in%20the%20real%20estate%20market%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20user%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6This%20is%20one%20of%20the%20sad%20realities%20of%20staying%20in%20Gujarat!%20Hope%20you%20and%20your%20family%20are%20fine!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVibes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20contacted%20Baldevbhai%20Patel%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20house.%20He%20admitted%20that%20Anirudh%20Kejriwal%20has%20given%20him%20a%20cheque%20of%20Rs%2035%20lacs.%20%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20want%20to%20get%20into%20details.%20I%20will%20be%20returning%20his%20amount%20soon.%20I%20will%20not%20be%20selling%20the%20house%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2Fsociety-denies-claims-owner-retracts-the-sale-offer-suddenly%2F%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2F%5C%22%3EVibes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709107243000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28124724%2FScreenshot-2024-02-28-at-12.47.13-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fjp-morgan-executive-alleges-caste-discrimination-in-gujarat-housing-complex%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20has%20been%20alleged%20that%20the%20housing%20complex%2C%20which%20has%20a%20majority%20of%20'Patels'%2C%20did%20not%20want%20a%20non%20Gujarati%20with%20the%20surname%20'Kejriwal'%20buying%20a%20house%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fjp-morgan-executive-alleges-caste-discrimination-in-gujarat-housing-complex%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98The%20Unknown%20Soldier%E2%80%99%20Team%20Prepares%20for%20%E2%80%98Conflict%E2%80%99%20With%20Unknown%20Enemy%20That%20Puts%20Finland%20Under%20Military%20Threat%3A%20%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20More%20Current%20Than%20Ever%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709107200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FConflict.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235924295%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aku%20Louhimies%20and%20Andrei%20Al%C3%A9n%20are%20readying%20for%20%E2%80%9CConflict.%E2%80%9D%20In%20the%20political%20and%20military%20thriller%2C