lented%26quot%3B%20presenter%20who%20was%20allegedly%20murdered%20with%20his%20partner%20by%20a%20former%20lover.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A80%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fjesse-baird-tributes-paid-to-amazingly-talented-tv-presenter-and-his-boyfriend-after-bodies-found-13082681%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fjesse-baird-tributes-paid-to-amazingly-talented-tv-presenter-and-his-boyfriend-after-bodies-found-13082681%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fjesse-baird-tributes-paid-to-amazingly-talented-tv-presenter-and-his-boyfriend-after-bodies-found-13082681%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gulzar%2C%20Jagadguru%20Swami%20Rambhadracharya%2C%20and%20the%20Downfall%20of%20the%20Jnanpith%20Award%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28111408%2FUntitled-design-10-2.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Two%20eminent%20writers%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20Sanskrit%20scholar%20Jagadguru%20Swami%20Rambhadracharya%20and%20renowned%20lyricist%20Sampooran%20Singh%20Kalra%2C%20better%20known%20as%20Gulzar%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20selected%20to%20receive%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20highest%20literary%20honour%2C%20the%20Jnanpith%20Award%2C%20this%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20award%2C%20usually%20awarded%20to%20only%20one%20litterateur%20per%20year%2C%20has%20sparked%20controversy%20whenever%20it%20has%20been%20awarded%20jointly.%20Shrilal%20Shukla%20and%20Amarkant%20were%20honoured%20together%2015%20years%20ago%20in%202009%20while%20Gurdial%20Singh%20shared%20the%20award%20with%20Nirmal%20Verma%20in%201999.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Jnanpith%20Award%20was%20instituted%20in%201965%20and%20is%20operated%20by%20the%20Jain%20family%20that%20runs%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20task%20of%20publication%20and%20awards%20is%20handled%20by%20a%20trust.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20latest%20announcement%20made%20for%20the%20Jnanpith%20Award%20for%202023%20echoes%20the%20much-hyped%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99.%20The%20work%20of%20academies%20is%20often%20shadowed%20by%20governments.%C2%A0However%2C%20government%20interference%20is%C2%A0%20generally%20a%20hushed%20affair.%20However%2C%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20has%20sent%20ripples%20down%20the%20literary%20community.%20Questions%20are%20being%20raised%20about%20the%20integrity%20of%20Jnanpith%20with%20many%20wondering%20if%20it%20has%20chosen%20to%20compromise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDescribing%20Swami%20Rambhadracharya%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98renowned%20scholar%2C%20educationist%2C%20philosopher%2C%20preacher%20and%20religious%20leader%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20award%20committee%20has%20given%20details%20of%20his%20association%20with%20the%20Ramanand%20sect%20and%20his%20religious%20positions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20further%20stated%20that%20he%20knows%2022%20languages%2C%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98poet%20and%20writer%E2%80%99%20of%20many%20languages%20including%20Sanskrit%2C%20Hindi%2C%20Awadhi%2C%20and%20Maithili%2C%20and%20has%20authored%20more%20than%20240%20books.%20He%20is%20said%20to%20have%20composed%20four%20epics%2C%20two%20of%20which%20are%20in%20Hindi%2C%20and%20has%20written%20commentaries%20on%20religious%20texts%20and%20is%20a%20well-known%20expert%20on%20Tulsidas%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamcharitmanas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Modi%20government%20honoured%20him%20with%20Padma%20Vibhushan%20in%202015.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20fail%20to%20understand%20why%20the%20Jnanpith%20announcement%20did%20not%20mention%20that%20Swamiji%20has%20continuously%20faced%20physical%20challenges%20because%20he%20lost%20his%20eyesight%20when%20he%20was%20two%20months%20old.%20There%20is%20also%20no%20mention%20that%20he%20is%20close%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20who%20flew%20to%20Chitrakoot%20to%20inaugurate%20his%2010%2C000-page%20Ashtadhyay%20commentary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESwamiji%20had%20testified%20in%20favour%20of%20Ramlala%20Virajman%20in%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20dispute.%20He%20was%20among%20the%20initial%20%E2%80%98warriors%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%2C%20was%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20campaign%20to%20demolish%20the%20%E2%80%98tainted%20structure%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20went%20to%20jail%20too.%20He%20denigrates%20the%20leaders%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Congress%20by%20name%20and%20calls%20them%20%E2%80%98fools%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20is%20also%20known%20to%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.india.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fswami-rambhadracharya-initiates-yagna-with-the-intention-of-reclaiming-pok-heaps-praises-for-pm-modi-6657842%2F%5C%22%3Econtroversial%20statements%20regarding%20Pakistan%20occupied%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%20(PoK).%20Recently%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20the%20guardian%20of%20Ramjanmabhoomi%20Pranpratistha.%20He%20retaliated%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqkSAOYTSgYo%5C%22%3EJyotirmoy%20Shankaracharya%20for%20calling%20the%20%3Cem%3Epratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%20not%20scriptural%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20temple%20trust%20also%20kept%20reiterating%20that%20the%20consecration%20is%20taking%20place%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20Ramanandi%20sect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20tried%20to%20sift%20through%20online%20sources%20to%20search%20Swamiji%E2%80%99s%20work%20and%20found%20one%20of%20his%20partly%20Hindi%20poems%20which%20has%20been%20translated%20into%20English%20and%20Russian%20by%20a%20foreign%20disciple%20of%20his.%20The%20entire%20poem%2C%20which%20is%20Swamiji%E2%80%99s%20version%20of%20one%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERamcharitmanas%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20quotes%2C%20is%20available%20on%20Swamiji%E2%80%99s%20official%20Facebook%20page.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20admit%20that%20I%20have%20not%20read%20the%20Sanskrit%20or%20Hindi%20literary%20works%20of%20Swami%20Rambhadracharya.%20However%2C%20I%20did%20listen%20to%20one%20of%20his%20sermons%20on%20YouTube%20and%20it%20failed%20to%20impress%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20compiled%20lectures%20(not%20writings)%20of%20speakers%20like%20Swami%20Akhandanand%2C%20Swami%20Ramsukhdas%2C%20Acharya%20Tulsi%20and%20Maulana%20Waheeduddin%20Khan%20were%20far%20more%20convincing.%20Rajneesh-Osho%E2%80%99s%20storytelling%20is%20also%20full%20of%20literary%20quotes%20and%20jokes.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20does%20not%20seem%20logical%20to%20pit%20a%20saint%2C%20who%20was%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20temple%20movement%2C%20against%20literary%20figures%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20sermons%20or%20commentary.%20This%20is%20disrespectful%20even%20of%20a%20saint.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIronically%2C%20Swamiji%E2%80%99s%20nomination%20for%20the%20Jnanpith%20award%20was%20welcomed%20not%20by%20the%20literary%20community%20but%20by%20controversial%20figures%20like%20Baba%20Bageshwar%20Dham%20and%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chauhan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnames-of-indira-and-nargis-dropped-from-national-film-awards%5C%22%3E%20Names%20of%20%E2%80%98Indira%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Nargis%E2%80%99%20Dropped%20From%20National%20Film%20Awards%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%20Gulzar%2C%20the%20second%20nominee%20for%20the%20Jnanpith%2C%20is%20a%20prominent%20personality%20of%20Hindi%20cinema.%20He%20is%20a%20successful%20filmmaker%20who%20has%20made%20many%20interesting%20films%20and%20has%20expertise%20in%20scriptwriting%20and%20songs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20received%20the%20Filmfare%20Award%2022%20times%2C%20National%20Film%20Award%20six%20times%2C%20Dadasaheb%20Phalke%20Award%2C%20Padma%20Bhushan%20and%20even%20a%20Grammy%20and%20Oscar%20(with%20AR%20Rahman)%20for%20song-writing.%20He%20is%20a%20popular%20cine-lyricist%20and%20his%20poetry%20gained%20great%20fame%20after%20receiving%20the%20Sahitya%20Akademi%20Award%20for%20an%20Urdu%20short%20story%20collection%20in%202002.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20he%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20popular%20face%20of%20literature%20festivals%20in%20Jaipur%20and%20other%20cities.%20The%20series%20of%20so-called%20literary%20festivals%20has%20set%20up%20a%20market%20with%20mainly%20English%20publishers%2C%20writers%E2%80%99%20agents%20and%20renowned%20writers%2C%20politicians%2C%20actors%2C%20singers%2C%20and%20anchors.%20The%20market%20itself%20bears%20their%20expenses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20the%20glittering%20world%20of%20cinema%2C%20in%20these%20%E2%80%98literary%E2%80%99%20fairs%20too%2C%20people%20are%20more%20interested%20in%20getting%20a%20glimpse%20of%20popular%20figures%2C%20taking%20selfies%20with%20them%20or%20displaying%20their%20fashion%20sense%2C%20rather%20than%20expressing%20their%20love%20for%20literature%20(or%20rather%20books%2C%20because%20even%20a%20cookery%20book%20can%20be%20%E2%80%98launched%E2%80%99%20there).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20only%20concern%20is%20that%20perhaps%20the%20semblance%20of%20lit-fests%20has%20started%20influencing%20serious%20literary%20awards.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20been%20reading%20Gulzar%20sahab%20ever%20since%20his%20poetry%20collection%20was%20published%20in%20Hindi%20by%20his%20best%20friend%20Bhushan%20Banmali%20in%20the%201970s.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20romantic%20literature%20of%20Urdu%20and%20Punjabi%20had%20its%20own%20charm.%20But%20later%2C%20after%20the%20emotional%20phase%20of%20songs%20like%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EJab%20bhi%20ye%20dil%20udaas%20hota%2C%20Jaane%20kaun%20aas%20paas%20hota%20hai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EShaam%20ki%20aankh%20mein%20nami%20si%20hai%2C%20aaj%20phir%20aap%20ki%20kami%20si%20hai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20some%20deep%20poetry%20was%20felt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20yearning%20never%20ceased.%20The%20turmoil%20of%20society%20and%20politics%20did%20not%20become%20the%20concern%20of%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eghazals%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20poems.%20Even%20in%20romanticism%2C%20there%20was%20reiteration%20in%20different%20forms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBharatiya%20Jnanpith%20mentioned%20Swamiji%E2%80%99s%20birthplace%20as%20Jaunpur%20in%20its%20announcement%20but%20Gulzar%20sahab%E2%80%99s%20birthplace%20(Dina%2C%20Pakistan)%20was%20left%20out.%20In%20the%20introduction%2C%20his%20identity%20as%20an%20Urdu%20poet%20has%20been%20downplayed%20and%20mentioned%20only%20after%20Hindi.%20The%20introduction%20goes%3A%20%E2%80%98Sampooran%20Singh%20Kalra%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20Gulzar%2C%20is%20a%20famous%20lyricist%20of%20Hindi%20films.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20he%20is%20a%20poet%2C%20screenwriter%2C%20film%20director%2C%20playwright%20and%20a%20famous%20poet.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20works%20are%20mainly%20in%20Hindi%2C%20Urdu%20and%20Punjabi%E2%80%A6%20Gulzar%20has%20been%20setting%20new%20milestones%20in%20the%20field%20of%20literature.%20In%20poetry%2C%20he%20invented%20a%20new%20genre%20%E2%80%9CTriveni%E2%80%9D%20which%20is%20a%20non-mukaffa%20poem%20of%20three%20lines.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrivenis%20were%20regularly%20published%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESarika%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20when%20Kamleshwar%20was%20the%20editor.%20Gulzar%20used%20to%20give%20the%20third%20verse%20a%20shocking%20twist%20which%20became%20like%20a%20game%20at%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20he%20is%20a%20good%20man%2C%20an%20accomplished%20filmmaker%20and%20a%20popular%20lyricist%2C%20there%20are%20more%20profound%20creators%20in%20literature%20than%20him.%20There%20has%20been%20some%20discussion%20on%20social%20media%20about%20this%2C%20though%20not%20enough.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHindi%20poet%20and%20editor%20Vishnu%20Nagar%20posted%20on%20Facebook%20that%20the%20neglect%20of%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Shukla%2C%20and%20other%20writers%20who%20have%20done%20great%20work%20and%20carved%20a%20niche%20in%20Hindi%20fiction%2C%20poetry%20and%20children%E2%80%99s%20literature%2C%20is%20disappointing.%20However%2C%20apart%20from%20Hindi%2C%20many%20prominent%20writers%20in%20other%20Indian%20languages%20are%20still%20beyond%20the%20realm%20of%20Jnanpith.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECritic%20Shambhunath%20has%20called%20it%20the%20%E2%80%98downfall%20of%20the%20Jnanpith%20Award%E2%80%99.%20Virendra%20Yadav%20believes%20that%20the%20devaluation%20of%20Jnanpith%20began%20when%20Shahryar%20was%20handed%20the%20award%20by%20Amitabh%20Bachchan.%20%E2%80%98In%20status%2C%20it%20has%20now%20become%20like%20a%20dustbin%E2%80%99s%20beauty.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20reading%20%E2%80%98lyricist%20Gulzar%E2%80%99%20written%20in%20the%20release%20of%20Jnanpith%20press%20release%2C%20writers%20began%20comparing%20the%20announcement%20with%20Bob%20Dylan%20getting%20the%20Nobel%20Prize.%20It%20does%20not%20seem%20appropriate%20at%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20his%20time%2C%20Dylan%20had%20shaken%20the%20conservative%20mentality%20of%20America%20with%20ideological%20excitement.%20Paired%20with%20American%20traditional%20music%2C%20his%20songs%20created%20a%20new%20political%20idiom.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBob%20Dylan%20raised%20his%20voice%20in%20favour%20of%20freedom%2C%20peace%20and%20justice.%20He%20wrote%20against%20war%2C%20nuclear%20threat%2C%20racism%20and%20slavery%2C%20sang%20against%20contempt%20and%20violence%20against%20the%20African-American%20community%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20whites%2C%20stood%20in%20support%20of%20protesters%20and%20their%20demonstrations%20in%20his%20compositions%20and%20gave%20strength%20to%20the%20voice%20of%20civil%20rights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDylan%2C%20in%20his%20entirety%2C%20was%20a%20voice%20of%20resistance.%20American%20society%20was%20in%20dire%20need%20of%20voices%20that%20could%20call%20out%20and%20say%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20and%20how%20many%20times%20must%20a%20man%20look%20up%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20he%20can%20see%20the%20sky%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20how%20many%20ears%20must%20one%20man%20have%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20he%20can%20hear%20people%20cry%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20and%20how%20many%20deaths%20will%20it%20take%20%E2%80%99til%20he%20knows%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20too%20many%20people%20have%20died%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20answer%2C%20my%20friend%2C%20is%20blowing%20in%20the%20wind!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20respect%20Gulzar%20%3Cem%3Esahab%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20an%20evergreen%20filmmaker%20and%20he%20is%20very%20fond%20of%20me.%20We%20often%20have%20many%20long%20chats%20regarding%20Kedarji%20(late%20Kedarnath%20Singh)%20and%20lit-fests.%20But%20i%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3En%20my%2050%20years%20of%20journalism%20and%2035%20as%20editor%20%E2%80%93%20where%20I%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20publishing%20a%20vast%20amount%20of%20literature%20in%20Hindi%20which%20required%20a%20close%20reading%20%E2%80%93%20I%20never%20saw%20Gulzar%20sahab%20taking%20on%20transformative%20concern%20and%20talk%20of%20the%20ills%20of%20society%20and%20politics%20in%20his%20songs.%20Romanticism%20can%20bring%20joy%20but%20after%20a%20certain%20period%20it%20becomes%20dull.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20not%20necessary%20that%20a%20courageous%20attitude%20in%20the%20subject%20one%20writes%20about%20would%20do%20away%20with%20the%20shortcomings%20of%20the%20craft.%20Only%20after%20such%20works%20get%20published%20can%20learned%20critics%20decide%20how%20much%20of%20it%20is%20poetry%20and%20how%20much%20is%20noise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGulzar%20would%20also%20agree%20that%20there%20are%20poets%20among%20us%20who%20write%20in%20different%20languages%20of%20the%20country%2C%20who%20have%20a%20stronger%20claim%20on%20the%20literary%20scale.%20By%20honouring%20them%2C%20the%20awards%20will%20gain%20recognition%20and%20credibility%20and%20boost%20their%20own%20pride.%20The%20rich%20tradition%20of%20Jnanpith%20has%20been%20no%20different%20but%20the%20recent%20turn%20of%20events%20has%20left%20it%20in%20darkness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20it%20is%20the%20era%20of%20%E2%80%98New%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20in%20which%20lyricists%2C%20stage%20poets%2C%20storytellers%20(one%20can%20even%20find%20all%20these%20qualities%20in%20one%20person)%20are%20awarded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAwards%20are%20not%20offered%20but%20procured%20nowadays.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fom-thanvi%5C%22%3EOm%20Thanvi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20who%20retired%20as%20editor%20of%20Jansatta%2C%20a%20Hindi%20daily%20of%20the%20Indian%20Express%20group%2C%20in%202015.%20He%20was%20the%20founding%20Vice%20Chancellor%20of%20HJ%20University%20of%20Journalism%20and%20Mass%20Communication%2C%20Jaipur.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F268702%2Fjnanpith-award-film-director-and-lyricist-gulzar-sanskrit-scholar-rambhadracharya%2F%5C%22%3EHindi%20orginal%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709103756000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28111408%2FUntitled-design-10-2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fgulzar-jagadguru-swami-rambhadracharya-and-the-downfall-of-the-jnanpith-award%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Questions%20are%20being%20raised%20about%20the%20integrity%20of%20Jnanpith%20after%20the%20announcement%20of%20this%20year's%20recipients%2C%20with%20many%20wondering%20if%20it%20has%20chosen%20to%20compromise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fgulzar-jagadguru-swami-rambhadracharya-and-the-downfall-of-the-jnanpith-award%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Joe%20Biden%20wins%20Michigan%20primary%20but%20faces%20voter%20backlash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709102460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-joe-biden-oval-office_6471646.jpg%3F20240228064850%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fjoe-biden-wins-michigan-primary-but-faces-voter-backlash-over-israel-policy-13082669%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Joe%20Biden%20has%20won%20Michigan's%20Democratic%20presidential%20primary%20-%20but%20has%20been%20hit%20by%20a%20significant%20protest%20vote%20from%20those%20angry%20at%20his%20support%20for%20Israel's%20military%20action%20in%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fjoe-biden-wins-michigan-primary-but-faces-voter-backlash-over-israel-policy-13082669%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fjoe-biden-wins-michigan-primary-but-faces-voter-backlash-over-israel-policy-13082669%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fjoe-biden-wins-michigan-primary-but-faces-voter-backlash-over-israel-policy-13082669%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Harassed%20Because%20of%20My%20Caste%2C'%20Says%20Dalit%20Govt%20Teacher%20Suspended%20Over%20'Saraswati%20Worship'%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28111137%2FUntitled-design-3-5.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJaipur%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Last%20month%2C%20a%20video%20of%20the%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations%20at%20a%20government%20upper%20primary%20school%20in%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Baran%20district%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20where%20a%20group%20of%20men%20could%20be%20seen%20arguing%20with%20Hemlata%20Bairwa%2C%20a%2040-year-old%20teacher%20of%20the%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBairwa%20belongs%20to%20a%20Dalit%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20month%20later%2C%20Bairwa%20has%20been%20suspended%20by%20the%20state%20education%20department%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20minister%20Madan%20Dilawar%2C%20and%20asked%20to%20report%20to%20duty%20in%20Bikaner%2C%20more%20than%20600%20kms%20from%20her%20home.%20The%20suspension%20of%20Bairwa%20has%20led%20to%20state-wide%20protests%20by%20Dalit%20groups%2C%20who%20are%20demanding%20the%20revocation%20of%20Bairwa%E2%80%99s%20suspension%20and%20resignation%20of%20the%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%20from%20January%2026%20this%20year%2C%20Bairwa%20can%20be%20seen%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20garlanded%20photos%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20Savitribai%20Phule%20and%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20while%20a%20group%20of%20men%20are%20confronting%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EBacchon%20ki%20devi%20to%3C%2Fem%3E%20Saraswati%20%3Cem%3Ehai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(the%20goddess%20of%20children%20is%20Saraswati)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20men%20are%20heard%20saying%2C%20to%20which%20Bairwa%20replies%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EBacchon%20ki%20devi%20toh%3C%2Fem%3E%20Savitribai%20Phule%20%3Cem%3Ehai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(the%20goddess%20of%20children%20is%20Savitribai%20Phule).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20men%20insist%20that%20Bairwa%20do%20a%20puja%20of%20the%20Hindu%20deity%20Saraswati%2C%20she%20is%20seen%20refusing.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20men%20assembled%20in%20front%20of%20the%20school%20are%20seen%20challenging%20her%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20programme.%20One%20of%20the%20men%20asks%20why%20there%20was%20no%20lamp%20and%20whether%20Bairwa%20is%20ignorant%20of%20Hindu%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20the%20meaning%20of%20Hindu%3F%20Hindu%2C%20Muslim%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Isai%3Cem%3E%20sab%20barabar%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Hindu%2C%20Muslim%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Christian%20are%20all%20equal)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bairwa%20is%20heard%20saying%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fkota-three-muslim-govt-school-teachers-suspended-over-forced-religious-conversion-of-students%5C%22%3EKota%3A%20Three%20Muslim%20Govt%20School%20Teachers%20Suspended%20Over%20%E2%80%98Forced%20Religious%20Conversion%E2%80%99%20of%20Students%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo%20FIRs%20lodged%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20incident%2C%20two%20FIRs%20%E2%80%93%20one%20by%20Bairwa%20against%20the%20men%20who%20had%20confronted%20her%20and%20the%20other%20against%20her%20for%20hurting%20religious%20sentiments%20%E2%80%93%20were%20registered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20Republic%20Day%2C%2026%20January%202024%2C%20while%20discharging%20my%20duties%20as%20a%20government%20servant%2C%20I%20was%20working%20in%20the%20school%20to%20celebrate%20the%2075th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20sacred%20Constitution%20of%20India.%20Hansraj%20Nagar%2C%20Radheshyam%20Nagar%2C%20Bharat%20Nagar%2C%20Kishan%20Nagar%20and%20other%20members%20of%20a%20same%20family%20of%20the%20village%20and%20teachers%20Hansraj%20Sain%20and%20Bhupendra%20Sain%20of%20the%20school%20staff%20started%20harassing%20me%20for%20Saraswati%20Puja%20in%20a%20public%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20FIR%20registered%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20Bairwa%E2%80%99s%20complaint%20at%20the%20Nahargarh%20police%20station%20in%20Baran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20female%20public%20servant%20from%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20(SC)%20category.%20Hansraj%20Nagar%2C%20Bharat%20Nagar%2C%20Radheshyam%20Nagar%20used%20casteist%20slurs%20and%20said%20that%20we%20will%20see%20you%20outside%E2%80%A6I%20have%20been%20feeling%20mentally%20scared%20since%20this%20incident%20disrupted%20the%20celebration%20of%20the%20national%20festival%20Republic%20Day%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20FIR.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20lodged%20by%20Bairwa%20adds%20that%20there%20is%20no%20mention%20of%20Saraswati%20Puja%20in%20Article%2028%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%2051(a)%20Imaginary%20things%20are%20prohibited%20from%20the%20scientific%20point%20of%20view%E2%80%A6.my%20fundamental%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20expression%20has%20been%20publicly%20violated%E2%80%A6The%20dignity%20of%20women%20has%20been%20violated.%20I%20demand%20strict%20action%20against%20anti-social%20elements%2C%20unconstitutional%20elements%2C%20anti-constitutional%20elements%2C%20elements%20against%20the%20father%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20Dr.%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar.%20The%20applicants%20are%20feeling%20unsafe%20after%20this%20incident%2C%E2%80%9D%20reads%20the%20FIR%20lodged%20by%20Bairwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20registered%20by%20Bairwa%20belong%20to%20various%20OBC%20caste%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20lodged%20by%20Bairwa%20has%20been%20registered%20under%20sections%20506%20(punishment%20for%20criminal%20intimidation)%20and%20504%20(Intentional%20insult%20with%20intent%20to%20provoke%20breach%20of%20the%20peace)%20of%20the%20IPC%20along%20with%20relevant%20provisions%20of%20the%20SC%2FST%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20and%20Circle%20Officer%20(CO)%2C%20Shahbad%2C%20Baran%2C%20Hemant%20Gautam%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20an%20FIR%20was%20also%20registered%20against%20Bairwa%20by%20locals%20in%20which%20she%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20hurting%20religious%20sentiments%20by%20her%20opinion%20on%20goddess%20Saraswati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20FIR%20against%20government%20teacher%20Hemlata%20Bairwa%20has%20been%20lodged%20by%20locals%20under%20sections%20including%20sections%20153A%20(Promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%2C%20race%2C%20place%20of%20birth%2C%20residence)%20and%20295A%20(Deliberate%20and%20malicious%20acts%2C%20intended%20to%20outrage%20religious%20feelings%20of%20any%20class%20by%20insulting%20its%20religion%20or%20religious%20beliefs)%20of%20the%20IPC.%20They%20have%20accused%20her%20of%20hurting%20religious%20sentiments.%20Investigation%20is%20being%20conducted%20for%20the%20FIR%20registered%20by%20Bairwa%20and%20also%20the%20one%20registered%20against%20her.%20No%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%20so%20far%20in%20either%20of%20the%C2%A0FIRs%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20CO%20Gautam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuspension%20after%20education%20minister%E2%80%99s%20public%20declaration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20January%2026%20incident%2C%20senior%20BJP%20MLA%20and%20Rajasthan%20Education%20Minister%20Madan%20Dilawarhad%20had%20said%20that%20an%20inquiry%20will%20be%20conducted%20into%20the%20incident.%20Bairwa%20was%20suspended%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20have%20got%20so%20pricey%20that%20even%20now%20they%20have%20not%20changed%20their%20ways%2C%20they%20say%20what%20role%20does%20Saraswati%20ma%20have%20in%20school.%20The%20person%20who%20has%20said%20this%20in%20this%20region%2C%20I%20suspend%20that%20person%20and%20make%20Bikaner%20that%20person%E2%80%99s%20office.%20I%20have%20given%20instructions%20to%20officials%20one%20hour%20back%20to%20suspend%20that%20person%20and%20make%20Bikaner%20the%20headquarters%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dilawar%20had%20said%20in%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Baran%20last%20week%20as%20the%20people%20assembled%20at%20the%20event%20hailed%20the%20decision%20with%20chants%20of%20Bharat%20Mata%20ki%20Jai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESixty-four-year-old%20Dilawar%2C%20who%20has%20been%20given%20the%20important%20portfolio%20of%20school%20education%20in%20the%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Sharma-led%20BJP%20government%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20himself%20belongs%20to%20the%20Dalit%20community%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20firebrand%20Hindutva%20faces%20of%20the%20saffron%20party%20in%20the%20state.%20He%20is%20often%20in%20the%20news%20for%20his%20statements.%20Ever%20since%20he%20has%20taken%20charge%20as%20education%20minister%2C%20he%20has%20been%20grabbing%20headlines%20for%20reasons%20such%20as%20his%20insistence%20on%20Surya%20Namaskar%20during%20morning%20assembly%2C%20calling%20Mughal%20emperor%20Akbar%20a%20%E2%80%98rapist%E2%80%99%20and%20with%20his%20statements%20against%20wearing%20Hijab%20in%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2023%2C%20the%20office%20of%20the%20District%20Education%20Officer%20(headquarters)%2C%20Elementary%2C%20Baran%20issued%20an%20order%2C%20which%20said%20that%20it%20has%20been%20decided%20to%20initiate%20disciplinary%20action%20against%20Bairwa%20and%20she%20is%20being%20suspended%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20with%20her%20headquarters%20being%20changed%20to%20Bikaner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98I%20am%20being%20targeted%20because%20of%20my%20caste%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Bairwa%20said%20that%20she%20is%20being%20harassed%20only%20because%20of%20her%20caste%20and%20that%20she%20will%20not%20be%20going%20to%20Bikaner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20Republic%20Day%20and%20I%20was%20doing%20my%20duty%20as%20per%20the%20constitution.%20At%20first%20two%20teachers%20of%20the%20school%2C%20Hansraj%20Sain%20and%20Bhupendra%20Sain%20pressurised%20me%20to%20worship%20Saraswati.%20Then%20they%20left%20and%20returned%20later%20with%20more%20villagers%20who%20started%20harassing%20me.%20They%20abused%20me%20with%20casteist%20slurs.%20Now%2C%20I%20have%20been%20suspended%20and%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20report%20at%20Bikaner%2C%20which%20is%20600%20kms%20away%20from%20my%20home.%20I%20have%20decided%20not%20to%20go%20there%20as%20I%20cannot%20accept%20this%20injustice.%20I%20am%20being%20harassed%20only%20because%20of%20a%20casteist%20mindset%20as%20I%20am%20from%20the%20scheduled%20caste%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bairwa%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBairwa%20also%20slammed%20minister%20Dilawar%20for%20announcing%20her%20suspension%20at%20the%20public%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20is%20it%20fine%20to%20threaten%20me%20on%20a%20public%20stage%3F%20I%20filed%20an%20FIR%20and%20yet%2C%20no%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%20till%20now.%20Instead%2C%20I%20have%20been%20suspended.%20Some%20of%20the%20accused%20regularly%20display%20casteism%20at%20the%20school%20where%20Dalit%20children%20face%20harassment%2C%E2%80%9D%20alleged%20Bairwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSavitribhai%20Phule%20opened%20schools%20for%20women.%20How%20many%20women%20were%20literate%20before%20her%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBairwa%20stood%20by%20her%20actions%2C%20and%20said%20that%20religious%20beliefs%20are%20personal%20and%20she%20only%20followed%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CReligious%20beliefs%20are%20personal.%20Be%20it%20the%20Constitution%20or%20a%20place%20such%20as%20schools%2C%20religious%20beliefs%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20here.%20How%20can%20the%20minister%20deliver%20a%20speech%20from%20a%20public%20stage%20saying%20that%20he%20is%20suspending%20me%3F%20This%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20respect.%20Are%20we%20his%20servants%20that%20he%20can%20announce%20our%20suspension%20from%20any%20place%3F%20I%20have%20done%20my%20work%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20I%20want%20justice%20and%20action%20against%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDalit%20groups%20protest%2C%20lock%20school%2C%20allege%20police%20action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20Bairwa%E2%80%99s%20suspension%2C%20Dalit%20groups%20across%20the%20state%20have%20been%20agitating%2C%20demanding%20that%20the%20decision%20be%20revoked.%20Members%20of%20Dalit%20outfits%20also%20held%20a%20dharna%20in%20front%20of%20the%20government%20upper%20primary%20school%2C%20Lakdai%20in%20Baran%20district%2C%20where%20Bairwa%20was%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalit%20groups%20alleged%20that%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20February%2027%2C%20that%20some%20protesters%20were%20injured%20after%20police%20allegedly%20used%20force%20on%20agitators%20sitting%20on%20dharna%20in%20front%20of%20the%20school.%20The%20Baran%20police%20denied%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20Rajasthan%20police%20destroyed%20the%20peaceful%20protest%20in%20support%20of%20Hemlata%20Bairwa.%20Hemlata%20was%20fired%20from%20her%20job%20by%20the%20Education%20Minister%20a%20few%20days%20ago.%20She%20had%20asked%20what%20was%20the%20contribution%20of%20Saraswati%20Devi%20in%20education%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fawz1obeRfP%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fawz1obeRfP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20The%20Dalit%20Voice%20(%40ambedkariteIND)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FambedkariteIND%2Fstatus%2F1762475055295176753%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2027%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSchoolchildren%20and%20Bhim%20Army%20members%20had%20locked%20the%20school%20gates%20and%20sat%20on%20dharna.%20Police%20beat%20the%20protesters%20with%20lathis%20which%20resulted%20in%20injuries%20to%20some%20of%20the%20agitators.%20We%20stand%20with%20Hemlata%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Till%20the%20time%20her%20suspension%20is%20not%20revoked%2C%20we%20will%20hold%20more%20protests.%20Ever%20since%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20come%20to%20power%2C%20officials%20from%20the%20SC%20and%20minority%20communities%20are%20being%20targeted.%20Education%20minister%20Madan%20Dilawar%2C%20who%20himself%20belongs%20to%20a%20Dalit%20community%2C%20has%20been%20given%20the%20ministerial%20post%20to%20target%20his%20own%20people%E2%80%A6We%20demand%20that%20Dilawar%20be%20removed%20from%20his%20ministerial%20post%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Anil%20Dhenwal%2C%20Rajasthan%20in-charge%20of%20the%20Bhim%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Baran%20police%20denied%20the%20allegations%20of%20lathi%20charge%20and%20said%20that%20the%20protesters%20were%20dispersed%20from%20the%20dharna%20site%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20avoid%20a%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20and%20the%20school%20was%20reopened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20exactly%20lathi%20charge%20that%20has%20taken%20place.%20Certain%20people%20had%20locked%20the%20door%20of%20the%20school%20and%20they%20were%20agitating%20over%20why%20the%20teacher%20Hemlata%20Bairwa%20was%20suspended%20and%20her%20headquarter%20changed%20to%20Bikaner.%20But%20their%20procedure%20of%20protesting%20was%20against%20law.%20They%20also%20misguided%20some%20students%20who%20said%20that%20the%20school%20should%20not%20be%20opened.%20Later%2C%20another%20group%2C%20who%20were%20in%20favour%20of%20opening%20the%20school%20also%20reached%20the%20site.%20They%20said%20either%20police%20should%20open%20the%20school%20or%20they%20themselves%20would.%20It%20resulted%20in%20a%20tussle%20between%20the%20two%20groups%20and%20a%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20was%20about%20to%20arise%20as%20the%20two%20groups%20were%20about%20to%20fight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Baran%20SP%20Raj%20Kumar%20Chaudhary%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaudhary%20added%20that%20after%20trying%20to%20convince%20the%20two%20groups%2C%20the%20police%20had%20to%20intervene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalit%20rights%20activists%20say%20that%20the%20suspension%20of%20Bairwa%20has%20been%20done%20with%20malice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20suspend%20Hemlata%20Bairwa%20and%20to%20change%20her%20headquarters%20to%20Bikaner%20is%20unjust.%20The%20education%20minister%2C%20instead%20of%20answering%20her%20question%20about%20what%20contribution%20Saraswati%20had%20in%20education%2C%20took%20this%20action.%20If%20they%20felt%20bad%2C%20or%20took%20it%20as%20a%20challenge%2C%20they%20should%20have%20countered%20it%20by%20answering%20and%20not%20by%20taking%20action.%20Hemlata%20didn%E2%80%99t%20say%20anything%20wrong%20as%20even%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20same%20party%20as%20the%20education%20minister%2C%20too%20pays%20his%20tribute%20to%20Savitribai%20Phule%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bhanwar%20Meghwanshi%2C%20Rajasthan%20president%20of%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Union%20for%20Civil%20Liberties%20(PUCL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%88%20%E0%A4%AB%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AE%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%89%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B0%20%