hvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20first%20move%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Himachal%20legislature%20party%20headed%20by%20former%20chief%20minister%20Jai%20Ram%20Thakur%20met%20Governor%20Shiv%20Pratap%20Shukla%20this%20morning%20(February%2028)%20and%20urged%20him%20to%20allow%20for%20the%20division%20of%20votes%20before%20the%20state%20budget%20is%20passed%20today%20in%20the%20ongoing%20budget%20session%20so%20that%20the%20Congress%20can%20%E2%80%9Cprove%E2%80%9D%20its%20majority%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVirbhadra%20family%20amps%20up%20pressure%20as%20son%20resigns%20from%20Sukhu%20cabinet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20speculated%20that%20there%20is%20a%20coup%20of%20sorts%20in%20progress%20within%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20the%20outcome%20of%20infighting%20between%20Sukhu%20and%20Himachal%20Congress%20chief%20Pratibha%20Singh%2C%20wife%20of%20eight-time%20Congress%20chief%20minister%2C%20the%20late%20Virbhadra%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPratibha%2C%20it%20is%20believed%2C%20had%20been%20hoping%20for%20the%20CM%E2%80%99s%20post%20after%20Congress%20won%20the%20state%20election%20in%20November%202022%2C%20but%20the%20party%20instead%20made%20Sukhu%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20six%20MLAs%20who%20now%20are%20rebelling%20against%20the%20party%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20former%20loyalists%20of%20Virbhadra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20the%20turmoil%20within%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20the%20late%20Virbhadra%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20son%20Vikramaditya%20announced%20his%20resignation%20from%20the%20council%20of%20ministers%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20Sukhu%20government%20has%20%E2%80%9Chumiliated%20its%20own%20MLAs%20several%20times%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20media%20in%20Shimla%2C%20he%20said%20that%20it%20is%20not%20right%20for%20him%20to%20continue%20in%20the%20government%20in%20such%20circumstances.%20He%20said%20he%20has%20briefed%20the%20party.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20the%20party%20high%20command%20has%20to%20decide%20where%20Congress%20is%20headed%20next%20in%20Himachal%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThakur%20says%20Congress%20government%20has%20lost%20mandate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThakur%20told%20reporters%20after%20meeting%20the%20governor%20that%20the%20Sukhu%20government%20had%20lost%20its%20mandate%20to%20stay%20in%20power.%20He%20said%20the%20governor%20was%20apprised%20of%20latest%20political%20developments%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20assembly%20speaker%20did%20not%20entertain%20our%20demand%20for%20the%20division%20of%20votes%20despite%20the%20provision%20in%20the%20law.%20It%20was%20obvious%20that%20the%20CM%20is%20scared%20of%20since%20he%20does%20not%20have%20the%20numbers%20now%20to%20stay%20in%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thakur%20told%20reporters%20outside%20the%20Governor%E2%80%99s%20House%20in%20state%20capital%20of%20Shimla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Budget%20Session%20begins%20in%20some%20time%20from%20now%2C%20the%20state%20gears%20up%20for%20some%20degree%20of%20political%20drama.%20It%20is%20learnt%20that%20the%20Sukhu%20government%20is%20mulling%20the%20suspension%20of%20some%20BJP%20lawmakers%20before%20the%20passing%20of%20the%20budget%20to%20avoid%20a%20floor%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%AC%20%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B7%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%A7%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B7%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%A5%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B