s%20alien%20character%20in%20the%20movie%2C%20this%20puppy%20just%20appeared%20in%20our%20lives%20out%20of%20nowhere.%20We%20heard%20a%20dog%20crying%20but%20assumed%20that%20someone%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20had%20just%20brought%20a%20young%20pup%20who%20was%20crying.%20But%20by%208%20pm%2C%20however%2C%20I%20felt%20something%20was%20wrong.%20So%2C%20I%20stepped%20out%20of%20our%20home%20and%20finally%20found%20this%20black%20and%20white%20puppy%20wedged%20between%20a%20parked%20car%20and%20the%20wall%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20initial%20attempts%20at%20pulling%20this%20puppy%20out%20weren%E2%80%99t%20successful.%20Though%20injured%2C%20he%20was%20feisty%20and%20did%20not%20allow%20them%20to%20touch%20him.%20Gerry%20finally%20managed%20to%20pull%20this%20pup%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20struggled%20to%20find%20a%20vet%20on%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20Eve.%20We%20eventually%20found%20one%20but%20had%20to%20pay%20five%20times%20the%20rate%20to%20get%20them%20over%20to%20our%20locality%20and%20give%20it%20first%20aid.%20On%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20Day%2C%20all%20clinics%20were%20shut.%20We%20could%20only%20take%20PK%20for%20treatment%20on%20the%202nd%20(of%20January).%C2%A0Having%20a%20spinal%20compression%20and%20a%20broken%20leg%2C%20PK%20was%20paralysed.%20After%20much%20care%2C%20attention%20and%20physiotherapy%20for%20more%20than%20a%20month%2C%20PK%20started%20walking%2C%20running%20and%20playing.%20Although%20we%20were%20initially%20reluctant%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20adopt%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSnapinsta.app_331049538_8602486409823819_7158574811666658490_n_1080-1708958384.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Daaman%20Dog%20Shelter%20Home%20in%20Chennai%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSnapinsta.app_331049538_8602486409823819_7158574811666658490_n_1080-1708958384.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSnapinsta.app_331049538_8602486409823819_7158574811666658490_n_1080-1708958384-300x166.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSnapinsta.app_331049538_8602486409823819_7158574811666658490_n_1080-1708958384-500x276.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSnapinsta.app_331049538_8602486409823819_7158574811666658490_n_1080-1708958384-768x424.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FSnapinsta.app_331049538_8602486409823819_7158574811666658490_n_1080-1708958384-150x83.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343232%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22596%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESarah%20and%20her%20husband%20Gerry%20spend%20their%20days%20taking%20care%20of%20these%20dogs.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20mother%E2%80%99s%20wish%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20person%20who%20was%20delighted%20to%20see%20Sarah%20and%20Gerry%20adopt%20PK%20was%20her%20mother.%20After%20losing%20her%20father%20early%2C%20Sarah%20recalls%20how%20she%20was%20brought%20up%20by%20%E2%80%9Cthree%20strong%20women%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20her%20mother%2C%20grandmother%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Emaasi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(aunt).%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20strong%20and%20kind%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarah%20had%20also%20grown%20up%20with%20dogs%20and%20other%20pets.%20She%20had%20keenly%20watched%20her%20mother%2C%20aunt%20and%20grandmother%20feed%20them%2C%20groom%20them%20and%20love%20them%20like%20their%20own%20family%20members.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Sarah%20had%20no%20fear%20of%20dogs%20and%20nurtured%20a%20strong%20affection%20for%20them.%