al%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337481%2Fbaljeet-kaur-mountaineer-climber-mt-annapurna-everest-kilimanjaro-himachal-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecleaning%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20commonly%20used%20in%20households%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20floor%20cleaners%2C%20dishwashing%20liquids%2C%20and%20laundry%20detergents%20boasting%20of%20clothes%20whitening%20capabilities%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20contain%20a%20combination%20of%20cleaning%20agents%2C%20fabric%20whiteners%2C%20sodium%20silicate%2C%20and%20sodium%20sulfate.%20A%20study%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EChemosphere%3C%2Fem%3E%20scrutinised%2030%20such%20cleaning%20products%20and%20revealed%20that%20they%20may%20emit%20hazardous%20volatile%20organic%20compounds%20(VOCs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20analysis%20highlighted%20that%20many%20of%20these%20VOCs%20pose%20serious%20health%20risks%2C%20including%20damage%20to%20the%20respiratory%20system%2C%20heightened%20cancer%20susceptibility%2C%20and%20adverse%20effects%20on%20developmental%20and%20reproductive%20health.%20Furthermore%2C%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EEnvironmental%20Working%20Group%3C%2Fem%3E%20(EWG)%20cautioned%20that%20the%20fumes%20emanating%20from%20certain%20cleaning%20products%20could%20trigger%20asthma%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimran%20recounts%20that%20during%20the%20first%2010%20to%2012%20weeks%20post-lockdown%2C%20she%2C%20like%20many%20other%20mothers%2C%20found%20herself%20relying%20heavily%20on%20cleaning%20products%20at%20home.%20She%20scrubbed%20surfaces%20multiple%20times%20to%20maintain%20a%20COVID-19-free%20environment.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20using%20cleaning%20liquids%20for%20washing%20our%20vegetables%2C%20fruits%20and%20everything%20else%20at%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20hygiene%20took%20centre-stage%2C%20was%20it%20unknowingly%20causing%20more%20harm%20than%20good%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%