%20and%20drainage%20they%20need%20to%20thrive%20in%20the%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20gardening%20website%3Cem%3E%20indiagardening.com%3C%2Fem%3E%20suggests%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20early%20summers%2C%20amend%20the%20garden%20soil%20to%20enhance%20the%20water%20retaining%20capability%20as%20well%20as%20aeration.%20Use%20organic%20matter%20or%20compost%20as%20it%20improves%20water%20retention%20and%20is%20also%20beneficial%20for%20microbes%20and%20worms%20in%20the%20soil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20forget%20to%20prune%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETimely%20pruning%20your%20garden%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way.%20Remove%20dead%20or%20diseased%20foliage%2C%20and%20prune%20back%20overgrown%20branches%20to%20improve%20air%20circulation%20and%20prevent%20fungal%20diseases.%20Deadhead%20spent%20flowers%20to%20encourage%20continuous%20blooming%20and%20remove%20any%20weeds%20that%20may%20compete%20with%20your%20plants%20for%20water%20and%20nutrients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20Water%2C%20then%20water%20some%20more!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20scorching%20heat%20of%20the%20sun%2C%20ensuring%20your%20plants%20receive%20the%20appropriate%20amount%20of%20water%20is%20crucial.%20Opt%20for%20deep%20watering%20less%20often%20to%20promote%20deep%20root%20growth%20and%20enhance%20drought%20tolerance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20an%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20best%20way%20to%20gauge%20that%20is%20to%20water%20your%20plants%20in%20the%20morning.%20If%20the%20soil%20is%20dry%20again%20by%20evening%2C%20you%20know%20your%20plants%20need%20to%20be%20watered%20twice%20a%20day.%E2%80%9D%20The%20health%20of%20your%20plants%20also%20depends%20on%20what%20time%20you%20water%20your%20plants.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20avoid%20water%20evaporation%2C%20water%20your%20plants%20either%20in%20the%20morning%20or%20post-sunset%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20further%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20avoid%20over-watering%20your%20plants.%20To%20prevent%20this%2C%20check%20if%20the%20soil%20beneath%20the%20surface%20is%20still%20damp.%20If%20so%2C%20wait%20for%20some%20time%20before%20watering%20the%20plant%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E8.%20Keep%20those%20bugs%20away%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20temperature%20rises%2C%20pests%20become%20more%20active%20and%20become%20a%20threat%20to%20our%20garden.%20Monitor%20plants%20regularly%20for%20signs%20of%20damage%20or%20infestation%2C%20and%20take%20prompt%20action%20to%20address%20any%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-13-1708694092.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mulching%20is%20good%20to%20reduce%20risk%20of%20weeds.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-13-1708694092.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-13-1708694092-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-13-1708694092-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-13-1708694092-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-13-1708694092-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343065%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMulching%20is%20good%20for%20reducing%20the%20risk%20of%20weeds.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsider%20using%20natural%20or%20organic%20pest%20control%20methods%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20neem%20oil%20or%20insecticidal%20soap%20%E2%80%94%20to%20minimise%20harm%20to%20beneficial%20insects%